\id MRK  - Dobu NT [dob] -Papua New Guinea 1985 (web version -2013) 
\h MAKI 
\toc1 Tetela Boboꞌana Maki ꞌIꞌetoladina 
\toc2 Maki 
\toc3 Mk 
\mt2 TETELA BOBOꞌANA  
\mt1 MAKI  
\mt2 ꞌIꞌETOLADINA  
\ip Buki gete solanaya Yesu ꞌina guinuwa waiwaidi ꞌiemwasalidi, nate yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiewaiwai sinedi ga tomota ꞌediyega ꞌiula apwesedi, wate leꞌoasa yaudi ꞌigieboboꞌanedi, wate yagila be lisu ꞌiloinedi, ta ꞌitauya ola debanega. Boda sinabwadi ꞌieꞌenidi masula gidalina ꞌenega, ta Anuwa Tabu ꞌigieꞌesasena, ga wate ꞌana tolomugiyao ꞌidi onao ꞌiewaiwai sinedi, ta wate bubuna toꞌumalina ta ꞌana eꞌisa mwawasa ꞌiewaiwaisinedi.  
\c 1  
\s1 Yoni togiebapitaiso ꞌina loguguya  
\r (Madiu 3:1-12; Luke 3:1-9, 15-17; Yoni 1:19-28)  
\p
\v 1 Gete tetela boboꞌana Toꞌetoseyana Yesu, Tauna Yaubada natuna, tetelina ꞌana ꞌebe eꞌale.   
\p
\v 2 \x * \xo 1:2 \xt Mal 3:1; Lu 7:27; Ais 40:3\x*Lowaenei palopita Aisea Yesu manuna ꞌiꞌetoladina, ga Yaubada ꞌina ona ꞌisimanena, ꞌigwae:  
\p “Gete ꞌigu toepilialeale yaetune be ꞌinugana be manuyo ꞌeda ꞌikakali,  
\v 3 be sena mitawa daitaya\f + \fr 1:3 \fk mitawa daita: \ft Me Yudia ꞌidi mitawa kaukau be gulegulewa daisinamo, ta pwatula gidalina, be kaiwenao wate nigeya sinabwadi. \f* ꞌenana sinabwana ꞌenega ꞌida simana apwesa be ꞌida gwae, ‘ꞌInapwana ꞌina ꞌeda wada kakali ta wagiepaepalu.’ ”   
\p
\v 4 \x * \xo 1:4 \xt Gu 13:34; Lu 1:77\x*ꞌEnega Yoni togiebapitaiso nina ꞌiapwesa sena mitawa daitaya ga ꞌiguguya tomota ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “ꞌImi bubuna toꞌumalidi ꞌediyega wada nuwaꞌebuni be ꞌenega yada giebapitaisoemi ta Yaubada ꞌimi bubuna nidi ꞌida nuwataudi.”   
\p
\v 5 Ta tomota yauyaudi sena Yudia maiboꞌana ꞌenega be ꞌasa Yelusalema ꞌenega sidelima Yoni ꞌina guguya sabi nonona, ga ꞌidi bubuna toꞌumalidi sisimanedi, ga ꞌigiebapitaisoedi bwasi Yolidani ꞌenaya.  
\v 6 Yoni ꞌana ꞌoama yobai kameli unuununa tuga, ta ꞌana gadiwana kameli bwalana, ta ꞌana masulao bilolo be muꞌawa tuga.   
\p
\v 7 Ta Yoni ꞌiguguya ga ꞌigwae, “Tauna muliguyega ꞌimeemai ꞌisinabwa sinegu, ꞌenega nigeya ꞌilobwelobwenegu be ꞌaenaya yabwagobwago be ꞌana ꞌaelawa yaliꞌami.  
\v 8 \x * \xo 1:8 \xt Gu 1:5\x*ꞌAboꞌagu bwasiyega tuga yagiebapitaisoemi, ta tauna Yaluyaluwa Tabunega ꞌida giebapitaisoemi.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌana giebapitaiso  
\r (Madiu 3:13-17; Luke 3:21-22)  
\p
\v 9 Tuta gote ꞌenaya Yesu ꞌasa Nasaleta ꞌipilisinena, nate sena Galili ꞌenega, ga ꞌimai bwasi Yolidani ꞌenaya ga Yoni Yesu ꞌigiebapitaisoena.  
\v 10 \x * \xo 1:10 \xt Yo 1:32\x*Ta Yesu niꞌatu bwasiyega ꞌigayoꞌoyaꞌama ga ꞌiꞌitatuꞌe ta galewa ꞌiꞌitena ꞌiꞌegegena, ta Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌana ꞌita ꞌatuwa bunebune ꞌimwaꞌuta ꞌenaya.  
\v 11 \x * \xo 1:11 \xt Sam 2:7\x*ꞌEnega ꞌebweu ꞌenana galewega ꞌionama ꞌigwae, “ꞌOyo natuꞌaiꞌailigu, manuyo yagwausowala sinabwana.”   
\s1 Seitani Yesu ꞌitoona  
\r (Madiu 4:1-11; Luke 4:1-13)  
\p
\v 12 Gote ꞌenega ga Yaubada Yaluyaluwana Yesu ꞌietunena ga ꞌitauya mitawa daitaya,  
\v 13 \x * \xo 1:13 \xt Ib 4:15\x*ga ꞌasiyata poti gote ꞌena ꞌimiyana ta tuta nidi ꞌediya Seitani ꞌitoo waiwai be ꞌaene Yesu ꞌigiebeꞌu. Ta sena nina ꞌenaya yobai bosasa wate simiyami, ta aneloseyao Yesu siꞌitaꞌiꞌisina.   
\s1 Togomana site ata Yesu ꞌibwauyedi  
\r (Madiu 4:12-22; Luke 4:14-15, 5:1-11)  
\b  
\p
\v 14 \x * \xo 1:14 \xt Md 3:2\x*Ga tuta nina ꞌena Kini Elodi ꞌiloina ga ꞌenega Yoni deliya sisaꞌu luguyena ga muliyega Yesu ꞌiapwesa Galili, ga Tetela boboꞌana Yaubada ꞌenega ꞌiloguguyaena,  
\v 15 ꞌigwae, “Tuta niꞌatu ꞌiapwesama be Yaubada ꞌida etoloina ꞌedaya. ꞌEnega ꞌimi guinuwa toꞌumalidi ꞌediyega wada nuwaꞌebuni be Tetela boboꞌana wada emise.”   
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega ꞌebweu tuta Yesu ola Galili leꞌawinaya ꞌiwadawadaꞌe ga togomana siteluwa matasina ꞌiꞌitedi Galili olanaya ꞌidi gomana siyauyauye, ꞌadi esanao Saimoni be Anidulu.  
\v 17 Ga Yesu ꞌibwauyedima, ꞌigwae, “Wamuliyegu be yada gibubumi tomota ꞌadi togomanao.”  
\v 18 \x * \xo 1:18 \xt Md 19:27\x*Gote ꞌena ꞌidi gomana sipilisinena ga Yesu simuliyena.   
\p
\v 19 ꞌEnega ꞌiawadaꞌe nao tupwana ga Yemesa be Yoni, taudi Sebedi natunao, ꞌiꞌitedi wagaya ꞌidi gomana sigibugibudi,  
\v 20 ga ꞌibwauyedima, ga tamadiya ma ina topaisewao siebesinedi nada wagaya ta Yesu simuliyena.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌebweu tai ꞌenega yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiula apwesena  
\r (Luke 4:31-37)  
\p
\v 21 Ga muliyega simai ꞌasa sinabwana ꞌana esana Kapaneumi ꞌenaya, ga Sabateya Yesu anuwa tapwalolo ꞌena ꞌilugu ga ꞌieꞌita.  
\v 22 \x * \xo 1:22 \xt Md 7:28\x*Ta tomota maiboꞌadi nuwadi ꞌiowana ꞌina eꞌita manuna, ga sigwae, “Eꞌita gete palupaluna ta waiwaina, ta ꞌida loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌidi eꞌita nenetana.”   
\p
\v 23 \x * \xo 1:23 \xt Mk 5:7; Yo 6:69\x*Ta anuwa tapwalolo nina ꞌenaya ꞌebweu tai ꞌimiyami, ta tai nina ꞌenaya yaluyaluwa biꞌi lowa ꞌilugu ga ꞌimiyami, ꞌenega tai nina Yesu ꞌena ꞌibwau,  
\v 24 ꞌigwae, “Yesu, ꞌoyo goma Nasaleta, toꞌase ꞌalena ga ꞌumai ꞌemaya? Nuwanuwayo be ꞌaene ꞌuda peꞌuma, aga? Ta ꞌoyo saꞌi niꞌatu yamwalatonimu, ꞌoyo tuga Yaubada Natuna.”   
\p
\v 25 Ta Yesu ꞌiloinena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌUlosaꞌu be tai nate ꞌenega ꞌuapwesama.”   
\p
\v 26 ꞌEnega yaluyaluwa biꞌi tai nina ꞌigietaina ga ꞌidededela ta ꞌimagana toila ga muliyega yaluyaluwa biꞌi tai solanega ꞌiapwesa.   
\p
\v 27 ꞌEnega tomota maiboꞌadi silosuyaedi ga taudimo sienaidedi, sigwae, “Mwaꞌadega eꞌita auwauna gete? Gete tai nina ꞌina loinega yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiloiloinedi ta siematamatane.”  
\v 28 ꞌEnega Yesu tetelina silelewanena Galili senanao maiboꞌadi ꞌediya.   
\s1 Yesu toleꞌoasa yaudi ꞌigie boboꞌanedi  
\r (Madiu 8:14-17; Luke 4:38-41)  
\p
\v 29 Ta Yesu anuwa tapwalolo ꞌenega ꞌiapwesa ga Yemesa be Yoni maꞌenao sitauya Saimoni be Anidulu ꞌidi anuwaya.  
\v 30 Ga Saimoni lawana ooyaiyaiyega ꞌileꞌoasa, ꞌenega Yesu siemataluwena toleꞌoasa nina manuna.  
\v 31 Ga Yesu ꞌilugu ꞌenaya ga nimanaya ꞌigiyaina ga ꞌigietoolona, ga ꞌina leꞌoasa ꞌisaligogo. ꞌEnega waine nina ꞌiapwesa ga ꞌadi masula ꞌigibubuna.   
\p
\v 32 \x * \xo 1:32 \xt Md 4:24\x*Ta sinala niꞌatu ꞌisugusuguwa, ga tomota ꞌidi toleꞌoasao be taudi yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌediyega sileꞌoasa maiboꞌadi simeꞌedi Yesu ꞌenaya,  
\v 33 \x * \xo 1:33 \xt Mk 3:11-12; Gu 16:17-18\x*be wate ꞌasa ꞌana tomiyanao maiboꞌadi siegogonama ga anuwa nina matanaya sitoolo.  
\v 34 ꞌEnega toleꞌoasao yaudi be taudi yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌigie kabaleyedi maiboꞌadi Yesu ꞌigie boboꞌanedi. Ta yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌeguma ꞌiula apwesedi ꞌiꞌetobodedi be geyaꞌabo sisimasimane, manuna tauna simwalatonina.   
\s1 Yesu Galili senananaya ꞌiloguguya  
\r (Luke 4:42-44)  
\p
\v 35 \x * \xo 1:35 \xt Md 14:23; Lu 5:16\x*Ta ꞌenega gonamapumapuya\f + \fr 1:35 \fk gonamapumapuya: \ft Gonagona gidalina.\f* Yesu ꞌitoolo ga anuwega ꞌiapwesa ga tebweuna ꞌitauya mwatui daitaya ga ꞌisidasida Yaubada ꞌena.   
\p
\v 36 Ta Saimoni magosenao wate siapwesa ga Yesu siꞌebesena,  
\v 37 ga silobenaya ta sieonena, “Tomota yaudi nuwanuwadi ꞌoyo.”   
\p
\v 38 Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Tatatauya ꞌaina wate ꞌasa ꞌediya be yaloguguya. Gete manuna yamai.”   
\p
\v 39 \x * \xo 1:39 \xt Md 4:23-25\x*ꞌEnega Galili maiboꞌana ꞌiasakowasiyena ga ꞌidi anuwa tapwalolo ꞌediya ꞌiloguguya ta wate yaluyaluwa biꞌi tomota ꞌediyega ꞌiula apwesedi.   
\s1 Yesu tolepelo ꞌebweu ꞌigie boboꞌanena  
\p
\v 40 Ta tolepelo ꞌebweuna Yesu ꞌena ꞌimai ga ꞌiꞌaetulasaya ta ꞌisidena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEguma ꞌimu nuwanuwa nadigega, kapekapeyana be ꞌugie boboꞌanegu.”   
\p
\v 41 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌiꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyena ga nimanega tai bwalana ꞌigitoona ta ꞌigwae, “O boboꞌana! ꞌUda ꞌesasa!”  
\v 42 Ga tai nina ꞌana lepelo ꞌigumwala manini, ga ꞌiꞌesasena.   
\p
\v 43 \x * \xo 1:43 \xt 1 Loi 14:1-4\x*Ta Yesu tai nina ꞌiꞌena paꞌalena,  
\v 44 ꞌigwae, “ꞌUtatauya ta geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu wate yaita ꞌena ꞌusimasimanegu, ta esi palupaluna ꞌutatauya totaliya ꞌenaya be ꞌiꞌitayo, be ꞌenega ꞌimu taliya ꞌuꞌebwaya Yaubada ꞌena, toꞌase nadigega ꞌada loina Mosese ꞌenega, be ꞌenega tomota simwalatoniyo ꞌaene niꞌatu ꞌuꞌesasemu.”   
\p
\v 45 \x * \xo 1:45 \xt Mk 7:36\x*Ta tolepelo nina nigeya Yesu ꞌina loina ꞌiematamatane, ta tomota yaudi ꞌediya ꞌiesimasimana. ꞌEnega Yesu nigeya sawesawenaya ꞌiaꞌataꞌatamana ꞌasa nidi soladiya, ta ꞌenega ꞌitauya sena mwatui daitaya ga nada ꞌimiyamiya, ta tomota sena yaudi ꞌediyega sitauya ꞌenaya.   
\c 2  
\s1 Yesu tokweno ꞌigie boboꞌanena  
\r (Madiu 9:1-8; Luke 5:17-26)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌAsiyata ꞌaina sigumwala ga Yesu ꞌiila Kapaneumi ꞌenaya, ga alena sinonona ꞌaene Yesu niꞌatu ꞌiila limanama.  
\v 2 Ta ꞌenega pwalu sinabwana anuwa solanaya be wate ꞌawa ꞌatamaninaya siegogona, ga Yesu ꞌiguguya ꞌediya.   
\p
\v 3 Ta tokweno ꞌebweu simeꞌena ta ꞌana toꞌaalao site ata ꞌebe ꞌenoega siꞌaalinama,  
\v 4 ga sitoona be ꞌaene tokweno nina siluguye Yesu ꞌena, ta nigeya sawesawediya, manuna pwalu sinabwa wawasae, ꞌenega siꞌaala tuꞌeyena anuwa debanaya ga ꞌana ꞌatowa siꞌewayaulena, ta ꞌenega tokweno nina ma ꞌebeꞌenona sietabetabeyena ga Yesu matanaya sisaꞌuna.   
\p
\v 5 \x * \xo 2:5 \xt Lu 7:48\x*ꞌEnega Yesu niꞌatu tai nidi ꞌidi emisa ꞌimwalatonina ga tokweno nina ꞌieonena, “Natugu, ꞌimu bubuna toꞌumalidi ꞌadi nuwatau niꞌatu ꞌulobedi.”   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 2:6 \xt 1 Yo 1:9; Ais 43:25\x*Ta ꞌaina loina ꞌana toeꞌitao Yesu selabenaya simiyami ga ꞌina ona sinonona ga taudimo ꞌatediya sinuwanuwa,  
\v 7 “Yesu gete mwaꞌadega ga Yaubada ꞌena ꞌioopaꞌala? Manuna nigeya ꞌebweu yaita sawesawenaya be tomota ꞌidi bubuna toꞌumalina ꞌida nuwataudi, nate namo Yaubada sawesawenaya.”   
\p
\v 8 Ta Yesu niꞌatu ꞌatenaya ꞌidi nuwanuwa ꞌimwalatonina, ꞌenega ꞌieonedi, “Toꞌase manuna nate nadigega wanuwanuwaꞌesa?  
\v 9 Ta toꞌase wanuwena yada onae tokweno gete ꞌenaya be ꞌaene yada gwae, ‘ꞌImu bubuna toꞌumalina niꞌatu yanuwataudi,’ nai yada gwae, ‘ꞌUtoolo be ꞌimu ꞌebeꞌeno ꞌuꞌaali be ꞌutatauya’?  
\v 10 Ta wada mwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu Tomota Natuna,\f + \fr 2:10 \fk Tomota Natuna: \ft Yesu tauna ꞌieesena The Son of Man, ꞌana mwalatoi tomota tuga. Yesu taunamo ꞌieesena Tomota Natuna, ta ꞌina eꞌitao ꞌediyega tomota simwalatonina ꞌaene tauna Toꞌetoseyana Keliso. \f* be ma igu loina baleꞌuya be tomota ꞌidi bubuna toꞌumalina yanuwataudi.”  
\v 11 ꞌEnega tokweno nina ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu gete yaeonayo, ‘ꞌUtoolo be ꞌimu ꞌebeꞌeno ꞌuꞌaala be ꞌutatauya ꞌimu ꞌasaya.’ ”   
\p
\v 12 \x * \xo 2:12 \xt Md 9:33\x*Ta ꞌenega ꞌitoolo ga ꞌina ꞌebeꞌeno ꞌiꞌaalena ga boda matadiyega ꞌiapwesa. Gote ꞌena pwalu maiboꞌadi nuwadi ꞌiowana ta Yaubada situpuna, sigwae, “Guinuwa gete ꞌebe nuwaowana ga batuwa namo taꞌitena.”   
\s1 Yesu Libai ꞌibwauyena  
\r (Madiu 9:9-13; Luke 5:27-32)  
\p
\v 13 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌiapwesa limana Galili leꞌawinaya, ta wate pwalu siegogonama, ga ꞌieꞌita ꞌediya.  
\v 14 Ta ꞌina eꞌita ꞌilosalonina ga ꞌitautauya ga ꞌebweu takisi ꞌana toꞌewa ꞌiꞌitena ꞌina anuwa ꞌebe paisewa ꞌena ꞌimiyami. Tai nina Libai, ta tamana Alipio. Ga Yesu ꞌieonena, “Libai ꞌumuliyegu.” ꞌEnega Libai nina ꞌitoolo ga Yesu ꞌimuliyena.   
\p
\v 15 Ta muliyega Yesu ma ina tononoyao simai Libai ꞌina anuwaya sabi ꞌeꞌai, ga boda Yesu simuliyena, taudi takisi ꞌana toꞌewao be wate ꞌaidi totoꞌumalidi, ga Yesu ma ina tononoyao maꞌediyao simiyatowa.   
\p
\v 16 \x * \xo 2:16 \xt Md 11:19; Lu 15:1-2\x*ꞌEnega Palisi ꞌidi loina ꞌana toeꞌitao siꞌitena, ga Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌediya sienaida, sigwae, “Toꞌase manuna ꞌimi toeꞌita takisi ꞌana toꞌewao ta wate totoꞌumalidi ꞌaina maꞌenao siꞌeꞌai egogona?”   
\p
\v 17 \x * \xo 2:17 \xt Lu 19:10; 1 Ti 1:15\x*Ta Yesu ona gete ꞌinonona ga ꞌieonedi, “Taudi boboꞌadi geya nuwadi togileꞌoasa, ta toleꞌoasao esiya nuwanuwadi togileꞌoasa. ꞌAboꞌagu yamaiya nigeya topalupaludi manudi, ta totoꞌumalidi sabi lemedi.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina ona ꞌebotana manuna  
\r (Madiu 9:14-17; Luke 5:33-39)  
\p
\v 18 Ta Yoni ꞌina tononoyao be wate Palisiyao ꞌeꞌai ꞌenega siedidigula ꞌidi tapwalolo manuna, ꞌenega ꞌaina tomota Yesu ꞌena simai ga sieonena, sigwae, “Yoni ꞌina tononoyao be wate Palisiyao ꞌidi tononoyao siedidigula, ta mwaꞌadega ga ꞌenega ꞌimu tononoyao nigeya siediedidigula?”   
\p
\v 19 \x * \xo 2:19 \xt Yo 3:29\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ona semalimaliyega ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega, ꞌilobwenena be ai ꞌana toyoꞌoyao siedidigula ꞌabo toai meꞌolotona maꞌediya simiyami? Nigeya saꞌi! Manuna tauna maꞌenao maiboꞌadi siegwausowala.  
\v 20 Ta wanuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene tuta ꞌimeemai be toai nina ꞌipilisinedi, ꞌenega esi sinuwa mwau be siedidigula ta siꞌebotana.”   
\p
\v 21 \x * \xo 2:21 \xt 1 Ko 10:21; 2 Ko 6:16\x*Ta ꞌebweu wate onasemalimali ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi, ꞌigwae, “Nigeya sawesawenaya be kaleko auwauna senasenaminega ꞌoama kadekadelina tabwabwada, ꞌabona nai esabu nina ꞌiesabu toili.  
\v 22 Ta wate nigeya ꞌebweu yaita oine auwauna ꞌida siwena bwala ꞌebesiwa kadekadelidi ꞌediya, ꞌabona nai siꞌalasabudi be oine ta ꞌebesiwa ꞌadi mudala, ta esi tada siwai ꞌebesiwa auwau daisinamo ꞌediya.”   
\s1 Yesu Sabate ꞌana ꞌinapwana  
\r (Madiu 12:1-8; Luke 6:1-5)  
\p
\v 23 \x * \xo 2:23 \xt 2 Loi 23:25\x*Sabateya Yesu ma ina tononoyao bagula solanega sitauya ga tonono nidi witi atuna siꞌegitagedi ga siꞌenidi.  
\v 24 Ta Palisiyao siꞌitediya ga Yesu sieonena, sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, mwaꞌadega ga ꞌenega ꞌimu tononoyao Sabate ꞌana loina sileꞌoaleꞌoa?”   
\p
\v 25 \x * \xo 2:25 \xt 1 Sam 21:1-6\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Buki Tabu ꞌena siꞌetoladina Debida manuna be ꞌeguma wasawai, wada mwalatoni ꞌaene tauna magosenao sibotana sinabwana,  
\v 26 ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌina anuwaya ꞌilugu ga beledi etaetabuna ꞌiꞌewena ga siꞌenina. Beledi nina ma ꞌana loina ꞌaene totaliya dimo ꞌadi tagwala be sida ꞌani. Ta tuwa tuga sibotana, ꞌenega totaliya sinabwana, ꞌana esana Ebayada, ꞌitagwalena ga siꞌenina.”   
\p
\v 27 \x * \xo 2:27 \xt 2 Loi 5:14\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi wate, ꞌigwae, “Yaubada Sabate ꞌiꞌebwaꞌeda ꞌida boboꞌana manuna, nigeya ꞌaene ꞌimweluluida Sabate manuna.  
\v 28 Manuna ꞌaboꞌagu Tomota Natuna ta wate Sabate ꞌana ꞌinapwana.”   
\c 3  
\s1 Yesu tai nimameyomeyo ꞌigieboboꞌanena  
\r (Madiu 12:9-14; Luke 6:6-11)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega muliyega Yesu ꞌiila limana anuwa tapwalolo ꞌenaya ga nada ꞌebweu tai nima meyomeyona ꞌilobena.  
\v 2 \x * \xo 3:2 \xt Lu 13:14\x*Ta Palisiyao Yesu silomataꞌiꞌisi, be ꞌeguma tai nina ꞌigieboboꞌane Sabate ꞌenaya maꞌetamo ꞌenega sida eꞌewa.  
\v 3 ꞌEnega Yesu tai nina ꞌieonena, “ꞌUtoolo be ꞌulagama,” ga tai nina ꞌitoolo ga ꞌilaga.   
\p
\v 4 Ga Yesu ꞌinapwanao ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Gete ꞌigu enaida ꞌemiya: To guinuwa boboꞌana ꞌedaya? Sabate ꞌena talelema nai tagieꞌelouya? Taꞌetoseyana nai taloemwawasa?” Ga ꞌina ona nigeya sieꞌieꞌisa.  
\v 5 \x * \xo 3:5 \xt Md 9:13\x*Ta Yesu ꞌidune masimasiyedi ma ina gamwasowala ta ma ina nuwamwau ꞌidi debapaꞌala manuna, ga tai nina ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “Nimayo ꞌuyasitoto,” ga tai nimana ꞌiyasitotona ga ꞌiboboꞌana.   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 3:6 \xt Md 22:15-16\x*ꞌEnega Palisiyao ma idi gamwasowala siapwesa ga Elodi ꞌina bodao maꞌediyao siloiloina be mwaꞌadega Yesu sida loemwawasaꞌese.   
\s1 Boda Galili leꞌawinaya  
\p
\v 7 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌipilisinedi ga ma ina tononoyao sidolo Galili leꞌawinaya, ta pwalu sinabwana simuliyenama.  
\v 8 Boda nidi getedi Yesu alena sinononaya ta Galiliyega be Yudiaega be Yelusalemega be Idumea senanega be Yolidani mali senega ta ꞌaina ꞌasa nidi Taiya be Saidoni selabediyega siegogonama.   
\p
\v 9-10 Ta Yesu toleꞌoasao ꞌigieboboꞌanedi, ꞌenega toleꞌoasao yaudi siegigigilama sabi gitoona, ꞌenega Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌieonedi, “Waga manugu wameꞌe be ꞌabo tomota siegigigila wawasae yagegelu wagaya.”   
\p
\v 11 Ta tomotai nidi ꞌediya yaluyaluwa biꞌi siluguya, ꞌeguma Yesu siꞌitai, sibeꞌu sanamwaꞌuta matanaya ta sibwaubwau, sigwae, “ꞌOyo Yaubada Natuna.”  
\v 12 Ta Yesu ꞌiloina paꞌaledi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo wabwaubwau apwesa ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu Yaubada Natuna.”   
\s1 Yesu site tuwelo ꞌiesinuwedi  
\r (Madiu 10:1-4; Luke 6:12-16)  
\p
\v 13 ꞌEnega muliyega ꞌoyaya ꞌituꞌe ga ꞌina tononoyao nidi ꞌiesinuwediya ga ꞌibwauyedi ga situꞌema ꞌenaya,  
\v 14 \x * \xo 3:14 \xt Lu 9:1\x*ga ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌOmi wate tuwelo yaesinuwemiya be ꞌomi maꞌegwao tamiyami be muliyega yaetunemi ꞌaina sena ꞌediya be wada loguguya  
\v 15 ta waiwaiyega yaluyaluwa biꞌi tomota ꞌediyega wada ula apwesedi.”   
\p
\v 16 \x * \xo 3:16 \xt Yo 1:42\x*Ta ꞌadi esanao getedi: Saimoni (tauna wate ꞌieesena Pita);  
\v 17 \x * \xo 3:17 \xt Lu 9:54\x*ta wate Yemesa matasina Yoni, taudi Sebedi natunao, ta Yesu ꞌieesedi Bowanage (ta Bowanage ꞌana mwalatoi ꞌaene taudi ꞌatuwa wepalala nadigega);  
\v 18 ta wate Anidulu be, Pilipi be, Batolomiu be, Madiu be, Tomasi be, mali Yemesa tauna Alipio natuna be, Tadiasi be, mali Saimoni, tauna togewana ꞌebeloina manuna;  
\v 19 ta wate Yudasa Isikaliota, tauna maꞌetamo Yesu ꞌida sipupuye.   
\s1 Yesu ta Bielisibubi  
\r (Madiu 12:22-32; Luke 11:14-23, 12:10)  
\p
\v 20 \x * \xo 3:20 \xt Mk 6:31\x*ꞌEnega muliyega Yesu ꞌiila ꞌina ꞌasaya, ta boda sinabwa wawasae siegogona ꞌenaya ga nigeya sawesawenaya Yesu ma ina tononoyao sieyawaiꞌata be siꞌaꞌa.  
\v 21 \x * \xo 3:21 \xt Yo 10:20\x*Ta ꞌina susuyao sinonona ꞌaene Yesu nigeya ꞌida eyawaiꞌata, ꞌenega sitauya sabi ꞌauꞌewenama, manuna sinuwena ꞌaene, “Niꞌatu ꞌikabaleya.”   
\p
\v 22 \x * \xo 3:22 \xt Md 9:34\x*Ta loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌaidi niꞌatu Yelusalemega simwaꞌutama ga Yesu ꞌina paisewa sinabwana siꞌitenaya ga sigwae, “Tai gete ꞌietoguinuwa manuna Bielisibubi,\f + \fr 3:22 \fk Bielisibubi: \ft Yaluyaluwa biꞌiyao ꞌidi ꞌinapwana, ꞌebe matauta ta toꞌumalina, tauna Seitani ꞌana tolema, nai Seitani tauna. Lowa me Ekiloni sibwagobwago ꞌenaya.\f* yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌidi ꞌinapwana ꞌina waiwaiyega yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiula apwesedi.”   
\p
\v 23 ꞌEnega Yesu tomota nidi ꞌibwauyedima ga onasemalimaliyega ꞌieꞌita ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase manuna Seitani ꞌaene tauna ꞌana bodao ꞌediya ꞌida etalauwala?”  
\v 24 Ta wate ꞌigwae, “ꞌEguma ꞌebweu ꞌebeloina ꞌenaya tomotai siweweyala be taudimo silosalosaiya maꞌetamo ꞌebeloina nina ꞌineneneta be ꞌibebeꞌu.  
\v 25 Wate ꞌeguma susu ꞌebweuna ta siweweyala be taudimo silosalosaiya maꞌetamo sineneta be ꞌidi miya ꞌitoꞌumali.  
\v 26 Seitani wate nadigega, ꞌeguma ma gosenao taudimo silosaiya ꞌiabe ꞌina ꞌebeloina nina ꞌibebeꞌu be ꞌigugumwala.   
\p
\v 27 \x * \xo 3:27 \xt 1 Yo 3:8\x*“ꞌEbeꞌita gete tai waiwaina nadigega Seitani ꞌina anuwaya. Nigeya sawesawenaya ꞌebweu yaita ꞌilulugu be ꞌina gwegwe ꞌiloꞌewadi, ta esi ꞌeguma ꞌebweu tai balaeyega toewaiwai nina nimana be ꞌaena ꞌiyona nuganedi ta ꞌenega muliyega sawesawenaya ꞌilulugu ꞌina anuwaya be ꞌina gwegwe nidi ꞌiloꞌewadi.   
\p
\v 28 \x * \xo 3:28 \xt Ib 6:4-6\x*ꞌEnega gete yaeona ꞌaiꞌailimi ꞌaene tomota ꞌidi loegesiyao be ꞌidi ona toꞌumalina maiboꞌana Yaubada ꞌida nuwataudi,  
\v 29 ta ꞌabo yaita Yaluyaluwa Tabuna ꞌiꞌawa toꞌumaliyei, geyaꞌabo saꞌi Yaubada ꞌinuwanuwatau, ta gete bubuna toꞌumalina nina ꞌenaya ꞌida miyaataya.”   
\p
\v 30 Gete nadigega Yesu ꞌionaꞌesa manuna sionaona ꞌaene tauna ꞌina waiwai yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌenega.   
\s1 Yesu sinana be tasinao ꞌenaya simai  
\r (Madiu 12:46-50; Luke 8:19-21)  
\p
\v 31 \x * \xo 3:31 \xt Mk 6:3\x*ꞌEnega niꞌatu Yesu sinana ta tasinao simai ga ꞌatamanaya sitoolo, ta ꞌenega ona namo sietunena be ꞌaene Yesu ꞌida apwesama ꞌediya.  
\v 32 Ga tomota nidi Yesu selabenaya simiyatowa sieonena, “ꞌInapwana, sinayo be tasimwao waꞌita apwesa, ta nuwanuwadi ꞌoyo.”   
\p
\v 33 Ga Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Yaita sinagu ta yaisigedi tasigwao?”  
\v 34 Ga taudi nidi selabenaya simiyami ꞌiduneyediya ta ꞌigwae, “Gete taudi sinagu be tasigwao.  
\v 35 \x * \xo 3:35 \xt Yo 15:14\x*ꞌEnega ꞌeguma yaisigedi Yaubada ꞌina nuwanuwa simulimuliye taudi tasigwao be nuugwao be wate sinagwao.”   
\c 4  
\s1 Onasemalimali tolelewana manuna  
\r (Madiu 13:1-9; Luke 8:4-8)  
\p
\v 1 Muliyega wate Yesu ꞌiila limana Galili leꞌawinaya sabi loguguya ta boda sinabwana siegogona ꞌenaya, ꞌenega ꞌebweu waga ꞌidoedoe ꞌenaya ꞌigelu ga ꞌimiyatowa, ta pwalu leꞌawaya sitootoolo.  
\v 2 Ta Yesu onasemalimali yauna ꞌediyega ꞌieꞌita tomota ꞌediya, ꞌigwaegwae,  
\v 3 “Wanono! Tobagula ꞌebweu ꞌina bagulaya ꞌitauya ga witi atuna ꞌilelewanedi,  
\v 4 ga ꞌaina atu nidi ꞌedaya sibeꞌu, ꞌenega manuwa siꞌitedi ta simwaꞌuta ga siꞌenidi.  
\v 5 Ta ꞌaina sibeꞌu bwaꞌa logulegulewana ꞌenaya ga sitabwa manini, manuna bwaꞌa gidalina tuga,  
\v 6 ꞌenega ala ꞌitudimwedi ga siꞌoapelu, manuna lamudi nigeya bwaꞌa gonituna silobaloba.  
\v 7 Ta ꞌaina kwakwakwala ꞌediya sibeꞌu ga sitabwa enoenowa, ta nigeya kapekapeyana be siuuwa, manuna kwakwakwala ꞌiewaiwai ga ꞌididiemwawasidi.  
\v 8 Ta ꞌaina atu bwaꞌa boboꞌana ꞌenaya sibeꞌu ga sitabwa ta sisinabwa ga siuwa, ga ꞌaina teti, be sikisiti, be analedi.”  
\v 9 Ga Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEguma matenami ona gete wada nono.”   
\s1 Onasemalimali ꞌina apwesas ꞌalena  
\p
\v 10 Muliyega pwalu sidelisawala ga Yesu taunamo, ga ꞌaina tomota ta ꞌina tononoyao site tuwelo maꞌediyao simai ga Yesu ꞌena sienaida, sigwae, “ꞌImu onasemalimali nidi toꞌase ꞌadi mwalatoi?”   
\p
\v 11 \x * \xo 4:11 \xt 1 Ko 2:10\x*Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “ꞌOmi niꞌatu Yaubada ꞌemiya ꞌiꞌebwaya be ꞌina loina solaꞌaiꞌailidi ꞌana tomwalatoiyao, ta esi tomota yaudi nuwa potapotadi ga onasemalimali sinono,  
\v 12 \x * \xo 4:12 \xt Ais 6:9-10; Yo 12:40\x*ta ꞌana nuwasabwalena nigeya simwalamwalatoni, ta wate ꞌana mwalatoi siꞌebeꞌebese ta nigeya sawesawenaya siloba. ꞌEnega wate nigeya sawesawenaya ꞌidi loegesiyao ꞌediyega sinuwanuwaꞌebuni, be geyaꞌabo Yaubada ꞌinuwanuwataudi.”   
\s1 Onasemalimali tolelewana manuna ꞌana liꞌama  
\r (Madiu 13:18-23; Luke 8:11-15)  
\p
\v 13 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega ꞌigu onasemalimali gete nigeya wanuwanuwa sabwaleni, aga? Be mwaꞌadega ꞌaina onasemalimali gete nadigega wada nuwasabwalenidi?   
\p
\v 14 “Tobagula nina Yaubada ꞌina ona ꞌilelewanena.  
\v 15 ꞌAidi atu sibeꞌu ꞌedaya, ꞌatuwa nadigega tomotai Yaubada ꞌina ona sinonona, ta ꞌenega Seitani ꞌimai ga ona nina ꞌediyega ꞌiꞌewa yauledi.   
\p
\v 16 “Wate nadigega atu nidi bwaꞌa logulegulewana ꞌenaya sibeꞌubeꞌu, ꞌaene ꞌabo tomota nidi Yaubada ꞌina ona sinonoi ta ma idi gwausowala sitatagwala,  
\v 17 \x * \xo 4:17 \xt Kol 2:7\x*ta nigeya lamudi ꞌipaꞌapaꞌala, ꞌenega tuta gidalina namo ꞌenaya sida miyami, be ꞌabo to tuta ꞌenaya Yaubada ꞌina ona ꞌana emisa manuna mwau nai etalauwala silobai, sibeꞌu manini.   
\p
\v 18 \x * \xo 4:18 \xt Mk 10:21-22; 1 Ti 6:9-10\x*“Ta atu nidi kwakwakwala ꞌediya sibeꞌuya ꞌatuwa tomota nidi taudi Yaubada ꞌina ona sinonona,  
\v 19 ta esaesa be baleꞌu ꞌina yageyao ꞌadi nuwanuwa ꞌediyega Yaubada ꞌina ona sinuwa pupulena, ꞌenega nigeya sawesawenaya be siuuwa.   
\p
\v 20 “Ta atu nidi bwaꞌa boboꞌana ꞌena sibeꞌuya ꞌatuwa tomota nidi taudi ma idi ꞌatetagwala Yaubada ꞌina ona sinonona, ꞌenega uwadi boboꞌana ta yauna siuwaedi. ꞌAina uwadiyao teti, ta ꞌaina sikisiti, ta ꞌaina analedi.”   
\s1 Onasemalimali mayale manuna  
\r (Luke 8:16-18)  
\p
\v 21 Ta Yesu wate ꞌediya ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo mayale loeloeꞌabina tasaꞌusaꞌu kwaiye ꞌule nai sita ꞌediyega, ta esi ꞌatamanaya tasaꞌu be ꞌimaedana,  
\v 22 be ꞌenega yage nidi kwaikwaiyidi maꞌetamo maedana nina ꞌigieapwesedi be taꞌitadi.  
\v 23 ꞌEguma matenami ona gete wada nono.”   
\p
\v 24 \x * \xo 4:24 \xt Lu 6:38\x*Ta wate ꞌieonedi, “Wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi be ona wada nono ꞌaiꞌailidi, manuna ꞌeguma ꞌomi toꞌase waꞌebwaya, wate nadigega ꞌana eꞌisa waꞌewa, ta esi ma ꞌana loeposeyana.  
\v 25 Manuna ꞌeguma yaita ꞌenaya Yaubada ꞌina gwegwe ꞌimiyami, gwegwe nina ꞌiloeposeyane. Ta yaita ꞌenaya nigeya Yaubada ꞌina gwegwe ꞌimiyami, toꞌase ꞌena ꞌimiyami Yaubada ꞌenega ꞌiꞌewa yauledi.”   
\s1 Onasemalimali suwana manuna  
\p
\v 26 Ga Yesu ꞌigwae, “Yaubada ꞌina loina tomota ꞌediya ꞌatuwa nadigega suwana tai ꞌina tanowaya ꞌiasodi,  
\v 27 ta tai nina ꞌiꞌeno be ꞌitoolo ꞌasiyata be boiboiya, ta suwana nidi sitabwatabwa, ta nigeya ꞌimwalamwalatoni mwaꞌadega sitabwatabwaꞌesa.  
\v 28 Manuna bwaꞌa ꞌiloina ꞌidi tabwa be ꞌidi sinabwa be ꞌidi uwa manuna,  
\v 29 \x * \xo 4:29 \xt Et 14:15\x*be muliyega ꞌabo uwana ꞌimatuwa ꞌenega toni bagula nina ꞌieꞌale be ꞌisesoni.”   
\s1 Onasemalimali beno atuna manuna  
\p
\v 30 Yesu wate ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega Yaubada ꞌina loina onasemalimaliyega yada giemaedanaꞌese ꞌemiya?  
\v 31 Nai gete nadigega ꞌebweu kaiwe atuna ꞌenaya yada loesawaꞌiꞌi, nate beno, manuna beno atuna gidalina,  
\v 32 ta ꞌabo taasoi be ꞌitatabwa pwatula ꞌisinabwa sinedi, ta nalinao sinabwadi ꞌisaꞌudi, be nalinao yauyaukwidi ꞌediya manuwa ꞌidi newa siꞌabidi.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina onasemalimali yauna  
\r (Madiu 13:34-35)  
\p
\v 33 Yesu ꞌina loguguyao ꞌediya tuta yauna onasemalimali yauna ꞌediyega ꞌieꞌieꞌita, be ꞌenega ꞌabo tomota ꞌediya kapekapeyana sida mwalatoni.  
\v 34 \x * \xo 4:34 \xt Yo 16:25\x*Tauna tuta yauna onasemalimaliyega ꞌiloguloguguya pwalu ꞌediya, ta ꞌina tononoyao dimo ꞌediya onasemalimali nidi ꞌiliꞌaliꞌamidi.   
\s1 Yesu yagila be lisu ꞌiloinedi  
\r (Madiu 8:23-27; Luke 8:22-25)  
\p
\v 35 ꞌAsuinuwanuwaya Yesu ꞌina loguguya wagega ꞌilosalonina ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Wageluma be taabala mali esenaya.”   
\p
\v 36 ꞌEnega sigelu ga sigiseyana ga pwalu leꞌawaya sipilisinedi, ta ꞌaidi waga wate maꞌenao,  
\v 37 ga wediliya sinabwana ꞌitowama, ta lisu wagaya ꞌisiwasiwaꞌoyaꞌa ga ꞌiabe sidadamana.  
\v 38 Ta Yesu waga kuliginaya ꞌana gedu ꞌisaꞌuna ga ꞌiꞌeno mwataya, ta ꞌina tononoyao silowanowanona ga sigwae, “ꞌInapwana ꞌutoolo be ꞌulemeda. ꞌIabe tamwamwawasa!”   
\p
\v 39 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌitoolo ga yagila be lisu ꞌibaꞌedi, ꞌigwae, “Tuwa! ꞌUꞌemutuyo be ꞌusiwalowa!” ꞌEnega yagila ꞌipela ga bwagabwaga maiboꞌana ꞌisiwalowa.  
\v 40 \x * \xo 4:40 \xt Md 14:31\x*Ta ꞌina tononoyao ꞌediya ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase manuna wamatauta? Mwaꞌadega nigeya waemiemisegu?”   
\p
\v 41 \x * \xo 4:41 \xt Sam 89:9\x*Ta nuwadi ꞌiowana ga simatauta, ta taudimo ꞌediya sigwae, “To tai sana gete ga yagila be lisu ꞌenana siematamatanena?”   
\c 5  
\s1 Yesu yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiula apwesedi  
\r (Madiu 8:28-34; Luke 8:26-39)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega siabala ga silugu me Gelasine ꞌidi leꞌawaya,  
\v 2 \x * \xo 5:2 \xt Mk 1:23\x*ga wagega Yesu ꞌisuya dabalaya, ta tai ꞌebweu ꞌilobena mayaluyaluwa biꞌina ꞌina ꞌebemiya duluwa, ꞌenega ꞌiapwesama, ta duluwa nina tomota ꞌadi ꞌaliꞌali.   
\p
\v 3 Ta tai gete lowa tomota sitoo be ꞌaene sida yoni malakwa kainumu ꞌenega, ta nigeya sawesawediya,  
\v 4 manuna malakwa nidi nimanaya be ꞌaenaya tuta yauna ꞌilasalasadi ta nigeya ꞌebweu sawesawenaya be ꞌigiyai,  
\v 5 ta ꞌidena sinedi ga ꞌitauya mitawaya ta boiboiya be ꞌasiyataya ꞌaliꞌaliya be ꞌoyaya ꞌiemagamagana, ta tauna gulewega ꞌiunuunu.   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 5:6 \xt Mk 1:24\x*Ta tai nina niꞌatu ꞌedasolega Yesu ꞌiꞌitenama, ꞌenega ꞌipili ga Yesu matanaya ꞌilobwagoena,  
\v 7 ta ꞌimagana toila, ꞌigwae, “Yesu ye, ꞌoyo Yaubada Toewaiwai sana Natuna, toꞌase ꞌutootoo be ꞌuguinuwe ꞌeguya? Tuwa! Yaubada ꞌana esanega yasida ꞌemuya be geyaꞌabo ꞌuda giegieꞌelouyagu.”   
\p
\v 8 Ona gete ꞌiꞌinanena manuna Yesu niꞌatu ꞌieonena, “Yaluyaluwa biꞌi niyo tai gete ꞌenega ꞌuapwesama.”  
\v 9 Ta Yesu wate ꞌienaida yaluyaluwa nina ꞌena, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega ꞌamu esana?” Ga tauna ꞌigwae, “ꞌAgu esana Tomoyauyau, manuna mabodama tai gete solanaya ꞌamiyami.”  
\v 10 Ga ꞌisidasida gewagewana Yesu ꞌena ꞌaene geyaꞌabo ꞌasa gote ꞌenega ꞌietuetune apwesedi.  
\v 11 Ta sena gote ꞌenaya bawe yauna siduwaduwala ꞌoyaya.  
\v 12 Ta yaluyaluwa biꞌi nidi sisida Yesu ꞌenaya ga sigwae, “Uetunema be ꞌalulugu bawe gotedi ꞌediya.”   
\p
\v 13 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌitagwaledi ga yaluyaluwa biꞌi tai nina ꞌenega siapwesa ga bawe ꞌediya silugu, ꞌenega bawe nidi siekabaleya ga maiboꞌadi sipili bulibuliyasu ga babagega sisobu olaya ga sidamana. Ta bawe nidi ꞌadi yau nadigega tu tausani.   
\p
\v 14 ꞌEnega bawe ꞌadi toꞌitaꞌiꞌitao ꞌidi matautega sidena ga sitauya ꞌasaya, ga yage nidi siꞌitedi maiboꞌana sisimanedi ꞌasa sinabwana be ꞌasa gidalidi tomotenidi ꞌediya. ꞌEnega toniꞌasa nidi simai be ꞌaene taudi matadiyega sida ꞌita toꞌase ꞌiapwesa.   
\p
\v 15 Ta Yesu ꞌena simai ga tai nina bada siꞌitena, lowa yaluyaluwa biꞌi solanaya simiyami niꞌatu debana ꞌipalupalu ga ꞌoama ꞌiꞌotena ta ꞌimiyami. Gote ꞌena maiboꞌadi simatauta.   
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega toepilialeale nidi tomotai ꞌediya siemwasala mwaꞌadega tai nina ꞌiboboꞌanaꞌesa, ta mwaꞌadega bawe siesilaeꞌesa.   
\p
\v 17 Ta toniꞌasa nidi silolagata ga Yesu sieꞌidiꞌidiyena ꞌaene ꞌidi sena ꞌida pilisine.  
\v 18 ꞌEnega Yesu wagaya ꞌidolodolo sabi gelu, ta tai nina niꞌa ꞌigieboboꞌanena Yesu ꞌena ꞌisida, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, sawesawenaya yamuliyeyo?”  
\v 19 Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Nigeya sawesawenaya, ta esi ꞌuila be ꞌutatauya ꞌimu susuyao ꞌediya be Yaubada ꞌina ꞌatenuwaꞌoleꞌoleyega ꞌigieboboꞌanemuya ꞌuemwasali be sida nono.”   
\p
\v 20 ꞌEnega tai nina ꞌitauya ꞌebeloina Dekapoli ꞌana ꞌasa sanau ꞌediya ga Yesu ꞌina guinuwa waiwaina manuna ꞌietetela ga tomota maiboꞌadi sinonona ga nuwadi ꞌiowana.   
\s1 Yesu iine ꞌeluwa ꞌigieboboꞌanedi  
\r (Madiu 9:18-26; Luke 8:40-56)  
\p
\v 21 Ga Yesu ma ꞌana tomuliyao siabala limana, ga boda sinabwana siegogonama leꞌawa nina ꞌenaya.   
\p
\v 22 \x * \xo 5:22 \xt Mk 7:32; Lu 13:13\x*ꞌEnega ꞌebweu tai, ꞌana esana Yailo, tauna anuwa tapwalolo ꞌana toꞌitaꞌiꞌita, ꞌimai ga Yesu ꞌilobena ga matanaya ꞌibwagobwago,  
\v 23 ga ꞌisida waiwai, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, natugu mewainena ꞌana leꞌoasa ꞌimwau ꞌaiꞌaila, ta tauna gwama tuga, ta nuwanuwagu ꞌumama be ꞌuda gitoo be ꞌida boboꞌana, ta geyaꞌabo ꞌimwawamwawasa.”   
\p
\v 24 ꞌEnega Yesu maꞌiyana sitautauya, ga boda sinabwana simulimuliye ta siegigigila ꞌedaya.  
\v 25 Ta boda nidi soladiya ꞌebweu waine maꞌedi ma ina leꞌoasa. Leꞌoasa nina nate lalana ꞌidaudau yakwala tuwelo ꞌediya, ta tuga ꞌetamo ꞌidaudau.  
\v 26 Lowa togileꞌoasa yaudi ꞌediya ꞌina mani maiboꞌana ꞌiloegumwalina, ta saꞌi ꞌidi guinuwa ꞌenega nigeya ꞌida boboꞌana, ta esi ꞌana leꞌoasa ꞌisinasinabwa.   
\p
\v 27-28 \x * \xo 5:27-28 \xt Mk 6:56\x*Waine nina Yesu ꞌimuliyena manuna lowa tetelina ꞌinonona, ga ꞌatenaya ꞌinuwanuwa ꞌaene, “ꞌEguma tuga Yesu ꞌana ꞌoama namo yagitoo yada boboꞌana.” ꞌEnega ꞌiloselabena ga ꞌana ꞌoama ꞌigitoona  
\v 29 ga lalana ꞌina dau ꞌiyapasa manini, ta taunamo oona solanaya ꞌilotoona ꞌaene niꞌatu ꞌiboboꞌana.   
\p
\v 30 \x * \xo 5:30 \xt Lu 6:19\x*Ta Yesu niꞌatu ꞌilotoona ꞌaene waiwai ꞌenega ꞌiapwesa ga ꞌiasakowasi ga boda ꞌienaidedi, ꞌigwae, “Yaita ꞌagu ꞌoama ꞌigitoona?”   
\p
\v 31 Ta ꞌenega ꞌina tononoyao sieonena, “ꞌInapwana, niꞌatu ꞌuꞌitena boda siaꞌoabuꞌoabuyemu ta siegigigila, ga ꞌoyo ꞌuenaida, ‘Yaita ꞌigitoogu?’ ”   
\p
\v 32 Ta Yesu ꞌiloꞌita dadana tomota gamwagamwanidiya be ꞌida ꞌita yaita ꞌina waiwai ꞌena ꞌiabala.  
\v 33 Ta waine nina taunamo ꞌana boboꞌana niꞌa ꞌilobena ꞌimwalatonina, ꞌenega ꞌimai ga ma ina dedela ꞌina matauta manuna ꞌibeꞌu sanamwaꞌuta matanaya ga ꞌisimana ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌaene tauna ꞌiguinuwena.   
\p
\v 34 \x * \xo 5:34 \xt Mk 10:52; Lu 7:50, 17:19\x*Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Natugu, ꞌimu emisa ꞌenega ꞌuboboꞌana. ꞌUtoolo be ma imu gwausowala ꞌutatauya. ꞌImu leꞌoasa maiboꞌana niꞌatu ꞌigumwala.”   
\p
\v 35 Tuta nina Yesu ꞌionaona waine ꞌenaya ꞌaina tomota Yailo ꞌina anuwega ale simeꞌena, ga sigwae, “Natuyo niꞌatu yawasina ꞌigumwala, ta geyaꞌabo wate toeꞌita nina ꞌina tuta ꞌumudamudali.”   
\p
\v 36 Ta Yesu wate ale nina ꞌinonona ga Yailo ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo ꞌuꞌateꞌate saꞌala, ta esi ꞌuemisegu tuga.”   
\p
\v 37 ꞌEnega Yesu boda yauna ꞌiꞌetobodedi be geyaꞌabo simulimuliye, ta nate namo ꞌina tononoyao sitetoi maꞌenao, nate Pita be Yemesa matasina tauna Yoni  
\v 38 sitautauya ga Yailo ꞌina anuwaya siapwesa ga ꞌewabamu be dedoi sinabwana sinonona.   
\p
\v 39 \x * \xo 5:39 \xt Yo 11:11\x*Ta Yesu ꞌilugu ga ꞌieonedi, “Toꞌase manuna wadedoi ta waegalagalala? Gwama nigeya ꞌimwawamwawasa ta ꞌiꞌeno mwataya tuga.”  
\v 40 Ta siedagiyena. Ta esi Yesu ꞌipaꞌidi ga siapwesa, ta gwama tamana be sinana be ꞌina tononoyao sitetoi Yesu maꞌedi silugu gwama ꞌina ꞌebeꞌeno ꞌenaya.  
\v 41 \x * \xo 5:41 \xt Lu 7:14\x*Ta Yesu gwama nimanaya ꞌigiyaina ga ꞌigwae, “Talita kumi.” Ta ꞌana gibui, “Negeyo ꞌutoolo.”   
\p
\v 42 ꞌEnega ꞌitoolo manini ga ꞌiadadana, manuna ꞌana yakwala niꞌatu tuwelo ꞌilobena. Ta tamana be sinana nuwadi ꞌiowana ꞌaiꞌaila.  
\v 43 Ga Yesu ꞌiꞌetobodedi ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita ꞌena wasimasimana ꞌigu guinuwa gete manuna, ta esi gwama ꞌana masula wagibubu be ꞌiꞌaꞌa.”   
\c 6  
\s1 Me Nasaleta Yesu siguitoyasena  
\r (Madiu 13:53-58; Luke 4:16-30)  
\p
\v 1 Ta Yesu ꞌiila tauna ꞌina ꞌasaya, ga ꞌina tononoyao simuliyena.  
\v 2 \x * \xo 6:2 \xt Yo 7:15\x*Ga Sabateya ꞌidi anuwa tapwalolo ꞌena ꞌilugu ga ꞌitoolo ta ꞌieꞌieꞌita ga tomota sinonona, ta yauyaudi nuwadi ꞌiowana ꞌina mwalatoi be ꞌina guinuwa manudi, ga sigwae, “Tai gete mane ꞌenega ꞌina sinasinapu ꞌilobena? Ta wate guinuwa nidi waiwaidi nimanega ꞌiguinuwedi, mane ꞌenega ꞌina waiwai ꞌilobena?”   
\p
\v 3 \x * \xo 6:3 \xt Yo 6:42\x*Ta wate sigwae, “Tai gete toꞌabiꞌabi tuga aga? Ta sinana Meli, be tasinao Yemesa be Yosese be Yudasa be Saimoni be wate nuunao maꞌedao tamiyami, aga?” ꞌEnega tomota Yesu siguitoyasena.   
\p
\v 4 Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Palopitao ꞌadi ꞌamayaba silobaloba mali ꞌasa ꞌediya. Ta taudi ꞌidi ꞌasaya esiya nigeya ꞌadi ꞌamayabamo, manuna taudi ꞌidi buꞌunao be ꞌidi susuyao siguitoyasedi.”  
\v 5 Ta Yesu nuwana ꞌiowana manuna tomota nigeya siemiemise, ꞌenega nigeya kapekapeyana be guinuwa waiwaina bada ꞌida guinuwedi. Nate namo toleꞌoasao puꞌepuꞌedimo ꞌigitoodi ga siboboꞌana.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌietunedi sabi paisewa  
\r (Madiu 10:1, 5-15; Luke 9:1-6)  
\p
\v 6 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌisakowasi ꞌasa ꞌediya ta ꞌieꞌieꞌita.   
\p
\v 7 \x * \xo 6:7 \xt Lu 10:1\x*Ga ꞌina tononoyao site tuwelo ꞌibwauyedi ga ꞌiloinedi be ꞌaene ꞌeluwa ꞌeluwa sida sakowasi ꞌasa ꞌediya, ta wate loina be waiwai ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi be ꞌenega sawesawediya yaluyaluwa biꞌi tomota ꞌediyega sida ula apwesedi,  
\v 8 ga ꞌina guguya ꞌenaya ꞌiloinedi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu toꞌase waꞌewaꞌewa. Geyaꞌabo masula nai tana nai mani ꞌabwaga manuna. Nate namo ꞌimi ꞌetoguna nimamiya,  
\v 9 be ꞌami ꞌaelawa waꞌotedi, ta esi geyaꞌabo ꞌami ꞌoama ꞌeluwena waꞌoteꞌotedi.”   
\p
\v 10 Ta wate ꞌieonedi, “ꞌEguma to anuwa ꞌena sibwauyemi be ꞌena walulugu, anuwa nina ꞌena waeꞌowaga be ꞌana laba sena nina wapilisine.  
\v 11 \x * \xo 6:11 \xt Gu 13:51, 18:6\x*Ta saꞌi ꞌeguma ꞌasa ꞌaina ꞌediya waapwesa be tomota nidi nigeya siꞌauꞌauꞌewami ꞌidi anuwa ꞌediya be wate nigeya ꞌimi guguya sinoonodi, ꞌasa nidi nedilina ꞌaemiyega waloutuutu yauledi ta wapilisinedi, be ꞌenega waeꞌitadi ꞌaene ꞌiabe mwau ꞌediya ꞌiapwesa.”   
\p
\v 12 ꞌEnega ꞌina tononoyao nidi sisakowasi ꞌasa yaudi ꞌediya, ga siguguya be ꞌaene tomota ꞌidi bubuna toꞌumalidi sida guitoyasedi be sida nuwaꞌebuni,  
\v 13 \x * \xo 6:13 \xt Ye 5:14\x*ga yaluyaluwa biꞌi tomota ꞌediyega siula apwesedi, ga toleꞌoasao yaudi wate bunamega sieꞌabidi ga siboboꞌana.   
\s1 Yoni togiebapitaiso ꞌina mwawasa  
\r (Madiu 14:1-12; Luke 9:7-9)  
\p
\v 14 \x * \xo 6:14 \xt Md 16:14\x*ꞌEnega Yesu tetelina tomota silelewanena sena yauyauna ꞌediya ga Kini Elodi ꞌinonona. Manuna ꞌaina tomota sionaona ꞌaene “Yoni togiebapitaiso mwawasega niꞌatu ꞌitoolo limana ꞌenega ma ina waiwai ꞌiguiguinuwa.”  
\v 15 Ta ꞌaidi siona ꞌaene, “Tauna Ilaitiya.” Ta ꞌaidi wate sigwae, “Tauna palopita ꞌebweu ꞌatuwa gimi palopitao.”   
\p
\v 16 Elodi wate niꞌatu tetela ꞌinonona ga ꞌigwae, “Nai tauna Yoni togiebapitaiso. Lowa yaloemwawasina ta saꞌi ꞌitoolo limanaya.”   
\p
\v 17 Manuna lowa Elodi Yoni ꞌigiyaina ga deliya ꞌiyonina, ta Yoni ꞌana giyai ꞌalena nate ꞌebweu waine ꞌana esana Elodiyasa, nate Elodi tasina Pilipi mwanena ta Elodi ꞌiꞌoayena,  
\v 18 ta Yoni Elodi ꞌieonena ꞌaene, “Gote nigeya bubuna boboꞌana, manuna tasiyo mwanena ꞌuꞌoayena.”   
\p
\v 19 Ta Yoni ꞌina guguya gete manuna waine nina ꞌinuwa mwau ꞌaiꞌaila ga nuwanuwana be Yoni ꞌida loemwawasi, ta nigeya sawesawenaya  
\v 20 manuna Elodi ꞌiegagalena ꞌaene Yoni nina tai palupaluna ta Yaubada ꞌina toguinuwa ꞌebweu, ꞌenega Elodi Yoni ꞌiꞌamayabena ga tuta yauna Elodi nuwanuwana ga Yoni ꞌina ona ꞌinonona ta manuna ꞌiꞌatesaꞌala.   
\p
\v 21 ꞌEnega Elodi nina ꞌina ꞌasiyata tubuwa ꞌiapwesa ga Elodiyasa niꞌatu ꞌeda ꞌinuwa lobena Yoni ꞌana loemwawasa manuna. ꞌAsiyata tubuwa nina ꞌana weꞌiweꞌiyaya masulina siguinuwena ga ꞌaina ꞌowaga sibwauyedima sabi ꞌemasula. ꞌOwagao nidi gabemani ꞌadi toloinao be tolosaiya ꞌadi toanuganao ta ꞌaidi Galili ꞌasanao ꞌidi ꞌinapwanao.  
\v 22 Tuta nina Elodi ma ꞌana ꞌowagao siꞌeꞌai, Elodiyasa natuna mewainena ꞌiluguma matadiya ga lausega ꞌigie gwausowalidi. ꞌEnega Elodi gomagweine nina ꞌena ꞌiona oboboma ꞌaene “ꞌEguma to yage ꞌuesinuwa be ꞌusidegu yada tagwala ꞌemuya.”  
\v 23 Ga wate ꞌiona upaupa sawatamatamana ꞌenega ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila yaona upaupa toꞌase nai yada ꞌebwaꞌeyo, ꞌeguma nai ꞌuda sida be ꞌaene ꞌigu ꞌebeloina yada weyali manuyo.”   
\p
\v 24 ꞌEnega gomagweine nina ꞌiapwesa ga ꞌitauya sinana ꞌena ꞌienaida, ꞌigwae, “Sinagu, toꞌase ꞌimu nuwanuwa be kini ꞌenaya yada side?”  
\p Ta sinana ꞌigwae, “Kini ꞌueona ꞌugwae, ‘Nuwanuwagu Yoni togiebapitaiso bulubuluna.’ ”   
\p
\v 25 ꞌEnega gomagweine ꞌilomanini ga ꞌiila kini ꞌena ga ꞌigwae, “Nuwanuwagu gete tuga Yoni togiebapitaiso bulubuluna gaeba ꞌena ꞌusaꞌu be ꞌuꞌebwaꞌegu.”   
\p
\v 26 Ta Elodi ꞌinuwamwau ꞌaiꞌaila, ta nigeya kapekapeyana be ꞌiguitoyase, manuna niꞌatu ꞌisawa tamatamana ꞌowagao matadiya.  
\v 27 ꞌEnega deli ꞌana toꞌitaꞌiꞌita ꞌebweu ꞌiloinena be ꞌaene ꞌida tauya be Yoni bulubuluna ꞌida meꞌe. Ga ꞌenega toꞌitaꞌiꞌita nina deliya ꞌitauya ga Yoni ꞌotona ꞌiꞌupwena,  
\v 28 ga bulubuluna gaebaya ꞌiusena ga ꞌimeꞌena, ga gomagweine nina ꞌiꞌebwaꞌena, ta tauna ꞌiꞌewena ga ꞌitauyena sinana ꞌenaya.   
\p
\v 29 Ta Yoni ꞌana tomuliyao ꞌina esilae tetelina sinononaya ga simai ga Yoni kokowana siꞌewena, ga sisaꞌu ꞌaliꞌaliyena.   
\s1 Yesu pwalu ꞌieꞌenidi  
\r (Madiu 14:13-21; Luke 9:10-17; Yoni 6:1-14)  
\p
\v 30 \x * \xo 6:30 \xt Lu 10:17\x*Ta niꞌatu Yesu ꞌina topaisewao site tuwelo siilama ga Yesu ꞌena ꞌidi paisewa be ꞌidi eꞌita maiboꞌana sisimanedi.  
\v 31 Ta tomota yau wawasae simeemai ta siilaila ga ꞌenega nigeya kapekapeyana be Yesu ma ina tononoyao sieyawaiꞌata be siꞌaꞌa, ꞌenega ꞌieonedi ꞌigwae, “Sena getei tada pilisine be tada tauya sena mwatui daitaya be gote ꞌena tupwana waeyawaiꞌata.”   
\p
\v 32 ꞌEnega taudimo waga sigeluna ga sitauya ꞌebweu sena mwatui daitaya.   
\p
\v 33 Ta pwalu nidi Yesu ma ina tononoyao ꞌidi gelu siꞌitena ga siꞌinanedi, ꞌenega taudi be ꞌasa yaudi ꞌadi tomiyanao wate maꞌediyao ꞌedega sipili ga sigimiapwesa sena gote ꞌenaya.   
\p
\v 34 \x * \xo 6:34 \xt Md 9:36\x*Ta muliyega waga ꞌilugu ga Yesu ꞌisuya dabalaya ga boda sinabwana kaukauya ꞌiꞌitedi, ta ꞌiꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyedi manuna taudi ꞌatuwa nadigega sipiyao nigeya ꞌadi toꞌitaꞌiꞌitamo, ꞌenega ꞌilolagata ga sinasinapu yauna ꞌieꞌieꞌita ꞌediya.   
\p
\v 35 \x * \xo 6:35 \xt Mk 8:1-9\x*Ga ꞌasuinuwanuwaya ꞌina tononoyao simai ga Yesu sieonena, sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, sena gete mwatui daita ta niꞌatu sinala ꞌisugusuguwa,  
\v 36 ꞌenega pwalu getedi ꞌuda etunedi be sida ila be ꞌadi masula sida gimwane ꞌasao be anuwao selabediya ꞌediya.”   
\p
\v 37 Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Ta mwaꞌadega? ꞌOmi geyaꞌabo waeꞌenidi, aga?”  
\p Ta ꞌina tononoyao sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, nigeya sawesawemaya, manuna maiboꞌadi ꞌadi masula ꞌana maisa nai tu analedi kina nadigega.”   
\p
\v 38 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEisa beledi ꞌemiya? Watauya be waꞌebesa.” ꞌEnega niꞌatu silobena ga Yesu sieonena, sigwae, “Beledi nima ta iyana ꞌeluwa ꞌalobedi.”   
\p
\v 39 ꞌEnega pwalu ꞌiloinedi be maiboꞌadi simiyatowa boda be boda pwatulaya.  
\v 40 ꞌEnega siweyalidi ga simiyatowa, ꞌaina boda tomota ꞌadi yau analedi, be ꞌaina boda tomota ꞌadi yau pipiti nadigega.   
\p
\v 41 Ta beledi nima be iyana ꞌeluwa ꞌiꞌewedi ga galewaya ꞌiꞌitatuꞌe ta ꞌiona oboboma masula nidi manudi, ga muliyega beledi ꞌigitomwedi ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi be sida eguyaiye tomota ꞌediya. Wate iyana nadigega ꞌigitomwedi ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi ta ꞌenega sieguyaiyedi.  
\v 42 ꞌEnega maiboꞌadi siꞌai ga gamwadi ꞌipawa.  
\v 43 Ta beledi be iyana tupwatupwadi siegogonedi ga kodo tuwelo siloemaedi.  
\v 44 Toꞌeꞌai nidi taidimo ꞌadi yau paibi tausani nadigega.   
\s1 Yesu ola debanega ꞌitautauya  
\r (Madiu 14:22-23; Yoni 6:15-21)  
\p
\v 45 Ta muliyega ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiloinedi be wagaya sigegelu, ꞌigwae, “Wagegelu be wanugana Betesaida mali esenaya, ta ꞌaboꞌagu bada ꞌetamo boda yaemataluwedi be siila ꞌidi ꞌasaya.”   
\p
\v 46 \x * \xo 6:46 \xt Mk 1:35; Lu 5:16, 6:12\x*ꞌEnega sigelu ta Yesu pwalu ꞌietunediya, ta muliyega ꞌituꞌe ꞌoyaya sabi sidasida Yaubada ꞌena.   
\p
\v 47 Ga niꞌatu ꞌiboi, ta ꞌina tononoyao bwagabwagaya siꞌadaꞌadau, ta tauna saꞌi tebweuna dabalaya  
\v 48 ꞌiꞌitedi ꞌidi neya ꞌenega siloꞌameꞌame manuna yagila matadiyega ꞌimeema.  
\p Ta tomwa uliulitaya Yesu ola debanega ꞌitauyama be ꞌaene selabediyega ꞌialogedo be ꞌida pilisinedi.   
\p
\v 49 \x * \xo 6:49 \xt Lu 24:36-37\x*Gote ꞌena ꞌina tononoyao maiboꞌadi Yesu siꞌitena ola debanega ꞌimeemai ga sinuwena ꞌaene welabana,  
\v 50 ꞌenega simatauta ga sinanala.  
\p Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo wamatamatauta. ꞌAboꞌagu tuga, ꞌimi ꞌinapwana.”   
\p
\v 51 \x * \xo 6:51 \xt Mk 8:17\x*Ga wagaya ꞌigelu maꞌenao ga yagila ꞌipela.  
\v 52 Ta nuwadi ꞌiowana sinabwana, manuna Yesu ꞌina waiwai manuna nigeya sinuwanuwa sabwaleni. ꞌEguma tuta nina tomota yaudi ꞌadi beledi Yesu ꞌieguyai be ꞌalena sida mwalatoni be ꞌenega sida nuwasabwaleni, ta tuga nigeya simwalamwalatoni, manuna debapaꞌalidi.   
\s1 Toleꞌoasao ꞌigie boboꞌanedi sena Genesaleta ꞌena  
\r (Madiu 14:34-36)  
\p
\v 53 ꞌEnega siabala sena Genesaleta ꞌenaya ga leꞌawinaya silugu ga ꞌidi waga gote ꞌena siloomuna.  
\v 54 Ga tuta nina sisuya toniꞌasa Yesu siꞌinanena,  
\v 55 ta ꞌenega tomota nidi sipili ga sitauya ꞌasa maiboꞌana ꞌediya ga toleꞌoasao simeꞌedi ꞌebeꞌeno ꞌediyega be Yesu ꞌena sitauyedi to sena ꞌena sinonona ꞌimiyami.   
\p
\v 56 \x * \xo 6:56 \xt Mk 5:27-28\x*Ga Yesu ꞌisakowasi sena yauyauna ꞌediya, ꞌaina ꞌasa sinabwadi be ꞌasa gidalidi be ꞌebe bagula ꞌediya. Ta tomota yaudi ꞌidi toleꞌoasao simeꞌedi ga ꞌebe gimwane ꞌediya siyamwayamwa ta sisidena sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, kapekapeyana be toleꞌoasao getedi ꞌamu ꞌoama tupitupinamo sida gitoo?” Ga Yesu ꞌediya ꞌitagwala. ꞌEnega taudi ꞌana ꞌoama sigitoona siboboꞌana.   
\c 7  
\s1 Me Yudia tubudiyao ꞌidi bubuna  
\r (Madiu 15:1-9)  
\p
\v 1 Ta Palisiyao be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌaidi wate maꞌediyao Yelusalemega simai ga Yesu ꞌena siegogonama,  
\v 2 ga ꞌaina ꞌina tononoyao siꞌita lobedi siꞌeꞌai, ta nigeya nimadi siꞌutuꞌutudi.  
\v 3 Manuna Palisiyao be wate me Yudia maiboꞌadi ꞌidi bubuna tubudiyao ꞌediyega nate nadigega: Nugana nimadi siꞌutu ꞌaiꞌailidi be muliyega siꞌaꞌa.  
\v 4 Ta ꞌeguma ꞌebe gimwane ꞌenega simamai wate siꞌesiwe be ꞌenega siꞌaꞌa. Ta wate loina yauna tubudiyao ꞌediyega gaeba be keiga be ꞌulena ꞌadi ꞌutu manudi simuliyedi.   
\p
\v 5 ꞌEnega gete Palisiyao be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao nidi Yesu ꞌena sienaida, sigwae, “Toꞌase manuna ꞌimu tononoyao tubudao ꞌidi loina nigeya siꞌamaꞌamayabedi, ta manima baibailidi siꞌeꞌai?”   
\p
\v 6 \x * \xo 7:6 \xt Ais 29:13\x*Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌOmi tokabokabo. Lowaenei Aisea palopita manumi ꞌiona upaupa ꞌaiꞌaila, tuta nina Yaubada ꞌina ona ꞌiꞌetoladina gete nadigega:  
\p ‘Tomota getedi ꞌawadiyega siꞌamaꞌamayabegu, ta ꞌatediyega nigeya.   
\p
\v 7 Ta wate ꞌeguya sitapwalolo besobeso, manuna ꞌidi eꞌitao ꞌaboꞌagu nigeya ꞌeguyega, ta esi tomota tuga ꞌidi nuwenuwega.’ ”   
\p
\v 8 Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi wate, ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌimi bubuna toꞌumalina, ꞌenega Yaubada ꞌina loina wasaꞌu kwaiyena ta tubumiyao saꞌi ꞌidi bubuna wamulimuliyedi.”   
\p
\v 9 Ta wate ꞌigwae, “ꞌAene ꞌomi tomwalatoi ꞌaiꞌaila, ta nigeya! Manuna Yaubada ꞌina loinao waguiguitoyasedi ta esi tubumiyao ꞌidi bubuna wagiyaiꞌiꞌisidi.  
\v 10 \x * \xo 7:10 \xt Sia 20:12\x*Lowa Mosese Yaubada ꞌina loina ꞌisimanena, ꞌigwae, ‘Tamayo be sinayo ꞌuda ꞌamayabedi.’ Ta wate ꞌigwae, ‘ꞌEguma yaita tamana nai sinana ꞌiꞌawa toꞌumaliyedi, ꞌilobwenena be waloemwawasi.’  
\v 11 Ta ꞌomi ꞌimi eꞌita kabokabo gete nadigega, ‘ꞌAbo ꞌebweu yaita tamana be sinana ꞌieonadi ꞌigwae, “ꞌIgu gwegweyao niꞌatu yatagwaledi Yaubada ꞌenaya ga etaetabuna, ꞌenega nigeya sawesawenaya be yalememi.” ’  
\v 12 Gete ꞌimi loina ꞌenega tomota ꞌidi lema tamadiyao be sinadiyao ꞌediya waꞌetoꞌetobodedi.  
\v 13 Tubumiyao ꞌidi loina gete ꞌenega, be ꞌimi eꞌita wate yauna ꞌediyega, Yaubada ꞌina loina waeyage besobesoena.”   
\s1 Tomota ꞌadi gietoꞌumali  
\r (Madiu 15:10-20)  
\p
\v 14 ꞌEnega pwalu ꞌibwau limedima ga ꞌieonedi, “ꞌIgu ona gete maiboꞌami wanonodi be nuwami ꞌida sabwalena:  
\v 15 \x * \xo 7:15 \xt Md 12:34\x*Nigeya ꞌebweu toꞌase tomota taꞌeꞌani be sigiegie bailida, ta esi yage nidi ꞌatedega siapweapwesa sawesawediya be sigiebailida.”  
\v 16 (-)   
\p
\v 17 ꞌEnega Yesu ma ina tononoyao pwalu siebesinedi ga anuwaya silugu, ta ꞌenega ꞌina tononoyao sienaidena, sigwae, “Kapekapeyana ꞌimu onasemalimali nina tomota ꞌediya ꞌuda liꞌami ꞌemaya?”   
\p
\v 18 Ga Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Nai ꞌomi wate nuwami nigeya ꞌisabwasabwalena, aga? ꞌEnega nigeya wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene toꞌase taꞌaꞌani be ꞌilulugu soladaya nigeya saꞌi ꞌida giebailida,  
\v 19 manuna nigeya ꞌatedaya ꞌitauya ta esiya gamwada namo ꞌena ꞌilugu be muliyega ꞌitatauya sumwana ꞌenaya.” (Yesu ꞌina eꞌita gete ꞌana mwalatoi ꞌaene nigeya ꞌebweu wate masula etaetabuna, ta esi maiboꞌana tada ꞌani.)   
\p
\v 20 Ta Yesu wate ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase tomota ꞌatediyega siapweapwesa sawesawediya be sigiebailidi,  
\v 21 \x * \xo 7:21 \xt Ga 5:19-21\x*nadigega nuwanuwa toꞌumalidi be loyawe, ꞌipwala, loemwawasa,  
\v 22 loelata, yalakwaiya, gamwasowala, kabo, sogala, eꞌipiꞌipi, sinala, gagasa be bubuna besobeso.  
\v 23 Gete yage nidi toꞌumalidi tomota soladiyega siapweapwesa ga sigiegie bailidi.”   
\s1 ꞌEbweu waine ꞌina emisa Yesu ꞌena  
\r (Madiu 15:21-28)  
\p
\v 24 Ga gote ꞌenega Yesu ꞌitoolo ga ꞌitauya Taiya be Saidoni senadiyao ꞌediya ga ꞌebweu anuwa ꞌena ꞌilugu, manuna geya nuwana be tomota sida mwalatoni ꞌina mai manuna, ta saꞌi nigeya kapekapeyana be ꞌimiya kwaiya  
\v 25-26 \x * \xo 7:25-26 \xt Mk 9:17-18\x*manuna ꞌebweu waine Yesu ꞌina mai tetelina ꞌinonona. Ta waine nina nigeya waine Yudia ta esi tauna goma Pinisia sena Silia solanega, ga natuna mewainena niꞌatu yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌigie toꞌumaliyena, ꞌenega sinanana ꞌimai ga Yesu ꞌaenaya ꞌibwago sanamwaꞌuta, ga ꞌisidena be ꞌaene yaluyaluwa biꞌi nina natuna ꞌenega ꞌida ula apwese.   
\p
\v 27 Ga Yesu ꞌigwae, “ꞌIlobwenena be gogama ꞌadi masula yada ꞌebwaꞌedi bemi, ta nigeya sawesawenaya be gogama ꞌadi masula yaꞌebwaya kedewa ꞌediya.”   
\p
\v 28 Ta waine ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌInapwana, ta saꞌi kedewa tuta yauna ꞌebe ꞌeꞌai ꞌagalaunega gogama ꞌadi masula mugumuguna ꞌenega siꞌeꞌa.”   
\p
\v 29 \x * \xo 7:29 \xt Yo 4:50-51\x*Ga Yesu ꞌigwae, “Kagutoki! Nate ona ꞌaiꞌaila. ꞌEnega ꞌutoolo be ꞌuila ꞌimu anuwaya. Yaluyaluwa biꞌi natuyo ꞌenega niꞌatu ꞌiapwesa, ga ꞌiboboꞌana.”  
\v 30 ꞌEnega ꞌitoolo ga ꞌitauya ꞌina anuwaya ga natunana ꞌilobena ꞌina ꞌebeꞌeno ꞌena, niꞌatu ꞌiboboꞌana.   
\s1 Yesu totenatui ꞌigie boboꞌanena  
\p
\v 31 ꞌEnega Yesu Taiya ꞌipilisinena ga ꞌitauya Saidoni, ta wate ꞌiataona Dekapoli senanao ꞌediyega ga ꞌiapwesa Galili olana ꞌenaya.  
\v 32 \x * \xo 7:32 \xt Mk 5:23\x*Ga ꞌebweu tai simeꞌena Yesu ꞌenaya tauna totenatui ta wate meya lidolidona ga Yesu sisidena be ꞌaene ꞌida gitoo be ꞌida boboꞌana.   
\p
\v 33 Ga Yesu tai nina ꞌiꞌauꞌewena ga boda ꞌediyega siadumaduma taudimo, ga Yesu nima matagigina tai tenanaya ꞌisaꞌu luguyedi ga muliyega tauna nimana ꞌigiwalina ga tai meyana ꞌigitoona,  
\v 34 ꞌenega Yesu ꞌiꞌitatuꞌe galewaya ga ꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyega ꞌionaona, ꞌigwae, “Epapata”, nate ꞌana gibui “ꞌUebwale.”  
\v 35 ꞌEnega tai nina tenana ꞌiebwalebwaledi ta wate meyana niꞌatu ꞌipalupalu be kapekapeyana ꞌiona ta ꞌinono palupalu.   
\p
\v 36 ꞌEnega Yesu tomota ꞌiꞌetobodedi be ꞌaene geyaꞌabo yaita ꞌena sida simasimane. Ta ꞌetoboda nina nigeya sinoono, ta esi siemwaemwasala dadanei tomota ꞌediya.  
\v 37 Ta taudi niꞌatu sinonona, nuwadi ꞌiowana sinabwana ga sigwae, “ꞌIna guinuwa maiboꞌana boboꞌana ta ꞌebe nuwaowana, manuna totenatui ꞌigienonoedi ta tomeya lidolido ꞌigie palupaludi be sioona.”   
\c 8  
\s1 Yesu boda ꞌieꞌenidi  
\r (Madiu 15:32-39)  
\p
\v 1 Tuta gote ꞌena boda sinabwana wate siegogonama Yesu ꞌenaya ta nigeya ꞌadi masulamo. ꞌEnega ꞌina tononoyao ꞌibwauyedima ga ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae,  
\v 2 “Tomota getedi yaꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyedi manuna niꞌatu ꞌasiyata ꞌetoi bada maꞌegwao ꞌamiyami ta nigeya ꞌadi masulamo.  
\v 3 ꞌEnega ꞌeguma mabotanidi yaetune iledi ꞌetamo ꞌedaya sitatai, manuna ꞌaidi ꞌedasolega simai.”   
\p
\v 4 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌina tononoyao sieonena, sigwae, “Mwaꞌadega sena mwatui daita ꞌena tomota yaudi getedi ꞌadi masula talobaꞌese?”   
\p
\v 5 Ta Yesu ꞌienaidedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEisa ꞌami belediyao simiyami?” Ga sigwae, “Sebeni namo.”   
\p
\v 6 ꞌEnega boda ꞌiloinedi be baleꞌuya simiyatowa, ga beledi sebeni nidi ꞌiꞌewedi ta manudi ꞌiona lokagutoki Yaubada ꞌena, ga ꞌigitomwedi ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi be tomota ꞌediya sieguyai, ga sieguyai sakowasiyedi.   
\p
\v 7 Ta ꞌaina iyana gidalidi wate simiyami, ꞌenega manudi Yesu ꞌiona oboboma, ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiloinedi be sieguyaiyedi wate tomota ꞌediya.   
\p
\v 8 ꞌEnega maiboꞌadi siꞌai ga gamwadi ꞌipawa, ga muliyega masula tupwatupwadi siegogonedi ga kodo sebeni siloemaedi.  
\v 9 \x * \xo 8:9 \xt Mk 6:44\x*Ta boda nidi ꞌadi yau powa tausani nadigega.   
\p
\v 10 ꞌEnega ꞌietune ilediya, ga ma ina tononoyao silomanini ga ꞌidi waga sigeluna ga Dalimanuta senanaya sitauya.   
\s1 Palisiyao nuwanuwadi weꞌiweꞌiyaya sida ꞌita  
\p
\v 11 \x * \xo 8:11 \xt Md 12:38; Yo 6:30\x*ꞌEnega Palisiyao simai ga Yesu ꞌena siegewagewana ga sitoona be ꞌaene weꞌiweꞌiyaya ꞌebweu ꞌida guinuwe manudi be sida ꞌawaꞌaiꞌaile ꞌaene ꞌina waiwai Yaubada ꞌenega ꞌimai.  
\v 12 Ta Yesu ma ina nuwamwau ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega ga ꞌenega ꞌepata gete ꞌomi nuwanuwami weꞌiweꞌiyaya, ta esi geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu wate weꞌiweꞌiyaya waꞌitaꞌita.”  
\v 13 ꞌEnega ꞌipilisinedi ga wagaya ꞌigelu limana ga siabala mali senaya.   
\s1 Elodi be Palisiyao ꞌidi eꞌita nadigega beledi ꞌana ꞌebe gieseseya  
\r (Madiu 16:5-12)  
\p
\v 14 Ta ꞌadi ꞌabwaga nigeya siꞌewaꞌewa manuna sinuwa pupuledi, ta beledi ꞌebweuna namo wagaya ꞌitupwa.  
\v 15 \x * \xo 8:15 \xt Lu 12:1\x*Ga Yesu ꞌiemataluwedi, ꞌigwae, “Palisiyao be Elodi ꞌadi beledi ꞌana ꞌebe gieseseya ꞌenega waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi.”   
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega tonono nidi taudimo ꞌediya sigwae, “Nai Yesu ꞌina ona ꞌalena gete, manuna ꞌada ꞌabwaga tanuwa pupulena.”   
\p
\v 17 \x * \xo 8:17 \xt Mk 6:52\x*Ta Yesu ꞌidi nuwanuwa niꞌatu ꞌimwalatonina ga ꞌieonedi, “Toꞌase manuna waonaona ꞌaene nigeya ꞌami ꞌabwagamo? Nate nigeya manuna yaonaona. Mwaꞌadega ꞌimi nuwanuwa sipotaya ga nigeya sawesawenaya be ꞌigu ona wasinapudi.  
\v 18 Mamatami ta saꞌi nigeya waꞌitaꞌita, ta wate matenami ta saꞌi nigeya wanoono, ꞌenega geyaꞌabo wanuwanuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌigu guinuwa pwaluyao ꞌadi ꞌeꞌai manuna aga?  
\v 19 \x * \xo 8:19 \xt Mk 6:41-44\x*Tuta nina beledi nima ꞌenega tomota paibi tausani yaeꞌenidiya, ta tupwa ꞌeisa kodo waegogonedi?” Ga sigwae, “Tuwelo.”   
\p
\v 20 \x * \xo 8:20 \xt Mk 8:6-9\x*Ta Yesu ꞌienaida wate, ꞌigwae, “Ga tuta nina beledi sebeni ꞌenega tomota powa tausani yaeꞌenidiya ta tupwa ꞌeisa kodo waegogonedi?” Ga sigwae, “Sebeni.”   
\p
\v 21 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ta ꞌomi sana nuwami nigeya ꞌisabwasabwalena.”   
\s1 Yesu tomata kebokebo ꞌigie boboꞌanena  
\p
\v 22 ꞌEnega Beteseida ꞌena simai, ga tai tomata kebokebo tomota siꞌauꞌewena Yesu ꞌenaya, ga sisidena be ꞌaene ꞌida gitoo be ꞌida boboꞌana.  
\v 23 Ta Yesu tomata kebokebo nina nimanaya ꞌigiyaina ta ꞌiꞌauꞌewena, ga ꞌasa nina ꞌenega siapwesa. ꞌEnega Yesu tai nina matana ꞌigiwalidi ta nimanega matana ꞌigitoodi ga ꞌieonena, “Sawesawenaya toꞌase ꞌuꞌitadi?”   
\p
\v 24 ꞌEnega tai nina ꞌiloꞌita dadana ga ꞌigwae, “Tomota yaꞌitedi, ta ꞌadi ꞌita ꞌatuwa nadigega kaiwe siloopili dadana.”   
\p
\v 25 Ta ꞌenega Yesu wate tai nina matana ꞌigitoo limedi, ꞌenega ꞌidune ga matana siꞌesasa ꞌaiꞌailidi, ga yage yauna ꞌiꞌitedi.   
\p
\v 26 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌietunena, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo ꞌuilaila ꞌasa sinabwana ꞌenaya, ta esi ꞌutatauya tauyo ꞌimu anuwaya.”   
\s1 Pita ꞌisimana Yesu manuna  
\r (Madiu 16:13-20; Luke 9:18-31)  
\p
\v 27 Gote ꞌena Yesu ma ina tononoyao sitautauya Sisalia Pilipai ꞌasanao manudi, ga ꞌedaya ꞌina tononoyao ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega tomota ꞌidi ona manugu ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu yaita?”   
\p
\v 28 Ga tonono nidi sigwae, “Tomota ꞌaidi siona ꞌaene ꞌoyo Yoni togiebapitaiso, ta ꞌaidi sigwae ꞌaene ꞌoyo Ilaitiya, nai gimipalopita ꞌebweu tuga.”   
\p
\v 29 \x * \xo 8:29 \xt Yo 6:69\x*ꞌEnega wate ꞌienaidedi, ꞌigwae, “Ta ꞌomi mwaꞌadega ꞌimi nuwanuwa ꞌaene ꞌaboꞌagu yaita?” ꞌEnega Pita ꞌilolagata ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌOyo Keliso, Toꞌetoseyana niyo.”   
\p
\v 30 Ta Yesu ꞌiloina paꞌaledi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita ꞌena wasimasimanegu.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌisimana ꞌina ꞌelouya ta ꞌina mwawasa manudi  
\r (Madiu 16:21-28; Luke 9:22-27)  
\p
\v 31 Ta wate ꞌilolagata be toꞌase maꞌetamo ꞌilobai ꞌieꞌitaena ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu Tomota Natuna maꞌetamo ꞌelouya sinabwana yaloba. Manuna ꞌinapwanao be totaliyao sinabwadi be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌiabe sieꞌidiꞌidiyegu be siloemwawasigu ta ꞌasiyata ꞌetoi mulinaya yada toololimana.”   
\p
\v 32 Yesu ꞌina ona gete ꞌenega ꞌisaꞌuapwese ꞌaiꞌailina ꞌina mwawasa manuna. ꞌEnega Pita Yesu maꞌalenaya ꞌitauyena ga ꞌiꞌetobodena be ꞌaene geyaꞌabo yage nidi siapweapwesa Yesu ꞌenaya.   
\p
\v 33 Ta Yesu ꞌiasakowasi ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiduneduneyedi ga ꞌiꞌenapaꞌala Pita ꞌena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌOyo Seitani, gete tuga ꞌupilisinegu! Manuna ꞌimu nuwanuwa tomota ꞌidi nuwanuwa, ta nigeya Yaubada ꞌina nuwanuwa nadigega.”   
\p
\v 34 ꞌEnega Yesu boda maiboꞌadi be ꞌina tononoyao maꞌediyao ꞌibwauyedima ga ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Yaita ꞌeguma nuwanuwana be ꞌimuliyegu, ꞌilobwenena be tauna ꞌina nuwanuwa ꞌida guitoyase be tauna ꞌana kelose ꞌiꞌaali be ꞌenega ꞌimwamwawasa, nate nadigega ꞌagu muliya nina ꞌana ꞌeda.   
\p
\v 35 “Ta ꞌeguma yaita yawasina ꞌiegagale, maꞌetamo yawasi nina ꞌiloseye. Ta ꞌeguma yaita manugu be tetela boboꞌana manuna yawasina ꞌitagwale be ꞌimwamwawasa, tauna ꞌiabe yawasina boboꞌana ꞌiloba.   
\p
\v 36 “ꞌEguma ꞌida esaesao baleꞌuya sinabwa wawasae talobadi nate yage besobeso, ta esi yage sinabwana nate yawasida boboꞌana.  
\v 37 Manuna ꞌeguma yawasida boboꞌana taloseyedi, nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌana lopaꞌelu ꞌimiyami.   
\p
\v 38 \x * \xo 8:38 \xt Md 10:33\x*“ꞌAboꞌagu Tomota Natuna, ta ꞌabo yaita ꞌoyo manugu ꞌuomayamaya ta wate ꞌigu eꞌita manuna ꞌuomayamaya be ꞌueyaseyaseyegu ꞌepata gete toꞌumalidi ta sogasogalidi matadiya, maꞌetamo yada eyaseyaseyo, tuta nina Tamagu ꞌina esaesa tuyatuyayalina ꞌenega yaila limanama, ta wate aneloseyao maꞌegwao.   
\c 9  
\p
\v 1 “Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi wate, ꞌigwae, “Yaona ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌemiya ꞌaene tomota ꞌaimi geyaꞌabo wamwawamwawasa ga ꞌana laba Yaubada ꞌina loina waiwaina ꞌida apwesa be wada ꞌita.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌana ꞌita dumadumana  
\r (Madiu 17:1-13; Luke 9:28-36)  
\p
\v 2 \x * \xo 9:2 \xt Mk 5:37\x*ꞌAsiyata sikisi mulinaya Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌetoi ꞌiꞌauꞌewedi, taudi Pita be Yemesa be Yoni, ga maꞌenao situꞌe ꞌoya ꞌebweu kesolana ꞌenaya, ga taudimo simiyami; ga siꞌitena Yesu maninina ꞌituyayala,  
\v 3 ta ꞌana ꞌoama ꞌiwakeke ꞌaiꞌailina, ꞌana ꞌita nigeya ꞌebweu yaita baleꞌuya sawesawenaya be ꞌoama ꞌida ꞌgieꞌesase be ꞌana wakewakeke nadigega.  
\v 4 Ta wate Ilaitiya be Mosese siapwesama ga Yesu nina maꞌedi siꞌawaꞌawa gwae.   
\p
\v 5 ꞌEnega Pita ꞌilolagata ga Yesu ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌida miya gete nadigega boboꞌana, ꞌenega ꞌimi yoeyoe ꞌetoi ꞌaꞌabidi, ꞌebweuna ꞌoyo manuyo, ta ꞌebweuna Mosese manuna, ta ꞌebweuna Ilaitiya manuna.”  
\v 6 Nate Pita ꞌionaona besobeso tuga, manuna magosenao simatauta.   
\p
\v 7 \x * \xo 9:7 \xt Md 3:17; 2 Pi 1:16-18\x*ꞌEnega pwana wate ꞌimwaꞌuta ga ꞌitala ekabobodi, ta pwana ꞌenega ꞌebweu ꞌenana sinonona, ꞌigwae, “Gete natugu boboꞌaiꞌailina, ꞌina onao wada nonodi.”   
\p
\v 8 Ta silomanini ga siloꞌita dadana ga Yesu tebweuna namo, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate yaita siꞌitaꞌita.  
\v 9 ꞌEnega ꞌoyega siebuebusima ga Yesu ꞌiloinedi, ꞌigwae, “Yage nidi niꞌatu waꞌitediya geyaꞌabo tomota ꞌediya wasimasimanedi ga ꞌana laba ꞌaboꞌagu Tomota Natuna mwawasega yatoolo limana.”  
\v 10 ꞌEnega yage nina sisaꞌu kwaiyena, ta taudimo sionaona, sigwae, “ꞌIna ona nina toololimana manuna mwaꞌadega ꞌana mwalatoi?”   
\p
\v 11 Ga Yesu ꞌena sienaida wate, sigwae, “Toꞌase manuna loina ꞌana toeꞌitao siona ꞌaene Ilaitiya ꞌigimi nuganama be muliyega Toꞌetoseyana nina ꞌimama?”   
\p
\v 12-13 \x * \xo 9:12-13 \xt Mal 4:5; Ais 53:3\x*Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “O nadigega, Ilaitiya ꞌaene ꞌida giminuganama be ꞌenega yage maiboꞌadi ꞌida giepaepaludi. Ta saꞌi Ilaitiya nina niꞌatu ꞌimai saba, ta esi tomota siguinuwa besobeso ꞌenaya toꞌase ꞌidi nuwena nadigega, nadigega Buki Tabu ꞌigimi simanaꞌesena. Ta wate ꞌaboꞌagu Tomota Natuna, toꞌase manuna Buki Tabu ꞌigimi simanegu ꞌaene ꞌelouya yaudi yalobadi be wate tomota sida guitoyasegu?”   
\s1 ꞌEbweu gwama ꞌana leꞌoasa lobwebwai manuna  
\r (Madiu 17:14-20; Luke 9:37-43)  
\p
\v 14 ꞌEnega ꞌoyega simwaꞌuta ga ꞌina tononoyao maiboꞌadi siloba limedi be boda yaudi maꞌediyao, ta wate loina ꞌana toeꞌitao wate maꞌediyao siegewagewana.  
\v 15 Ga tuta nina pwalu Yesu siꞌinanena nuwadi ꞌiowana sinabwana, ga ꞌenaya sipili manini sabi ꞌitana.   
\p
\v 16 Ta Yesu ꞌidi egewagewana manuna ꞌienaida, ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase manuna waonaona?”   
\p
\v 17 Ga ꞌebweu tai boda nidi ꞌediyega Yesu ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌidi egewagewana ꞌalena natugu, manuna ꞌina leꞌoasa ꞌenega nigeya kapekapeyana be ꞌiona,  
\v 18 ta ꞌaina tuta yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌina guinuwega ꞌitatai ta ꞌawanega busobuso siapweapwesa, ta ꞌiesalaꞌiꞌita be ꞌidededela. Ta ꞌimu tononoyao niꞌatu yasidedi be ꞌaene yaluyaluwa biꞌi gwama ꞌenega siula apwese, ta nigeya sawesawediya.”   
\p
\v 19 Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌOmi sana mwaꞌadega? Ga debami paꞌala yaita! Niꞌatu ꞌimi debapaꞌala ꞌenega yaloꞌameꞌame. Baga gwama nina wameꞌe ꞌeguya be yaꞌita.”   
\p
\v 20 ꞌEnega gwama nina simeꞌena ꞌenaya, ta yaluyaluwa biꞌi Yesu ꞌiꞌitena, ꞌenega ꞌiginao ga gwama ꞌitai ga baleꞌuya ꞌibeꞌu ga ꞌidededela ta ꞌawanega busobuso siapweapwesa.   
\p
\v 21 Ta Yesu gwama tamana ꞌieonena, “To tuta ꞌena ꞌina leꞌoasa ꞌieꞌale?” Ga tamana ꞌigwae, “ꞌIna tuta gwamega.  
\v 22 ꞌEnega ꞌabo ꞌitatai ꞌaina tuta ꞌibebeꞌu kaiwe ꞌalaꞌalasidi ꞌediya ta ꞌaina tuta bwasi niꞌudi ꞌediya be ꞌiabe ꞌiloemwawasi. ꞌEnega ꞌabo kapekapeyana ꞌuda ꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyema be ꞌulemema.”   
\p
\v 23 \x * \xo 9:23 \xt Mk 11:23\x*Ta Yesu tai nina ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “Niꞌatu ꞌuona ‘ꞌAbo kapekapeyana’, aga? Ta esi ꞌuda nuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene ꞌeguma taemisa, yage maiboꞌana kapekapeyana ꞌedaya.”   
\p
\v 24 \x * \xo 9:24 \xt Lu 17:5\x*Gote ꞌena tai nina ꞌiona toitoila, ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila yaemisa, ta nigeya emisa ꞌaiꞌaila. Nuwanuwagu be ꞌigu emisa ꞌugiewaiwaiye.”   
\p
\v 25 Ta Yesu boda yauyaudi sipilipilima ꞌiꞌitedi, ꞌenega yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiꞌenapaꞌalina, ꞌigwae, “ꞌOyo yaluyaluwa toꞌumaliyo ꞌimu lobwebwai ꞌenega gwama ꞌieuwauwa, yaloineyo be ꞌupilisine atae be geyaꞌabo wate ꞌebweu tuta ꞌulugulugu limana ꞌena.”   
\p
\v 26 ꞌEnega yaluyaluwa nina ꞌimagamagana ga gwama ꞌana lobwebwai ꞌiginaona ga ꞌidededela sinabwana, ta yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌenega ꞌiapwesa ga ꞌitauya. Ta boda gwama siꞌitena ꞌana ꞌita ꞌatuwa ꞌimwawasa, ga simatauta ta sigwae, “Niꞌatu ꞌimwawasa.”   
\p
\v 27 Ta Yesu gwama nimana ꞌigiyaina ga ꞌigietoolona, ta gwama nina ꞌitoolo, niꞌatu ꞌiboboꞌana.   
\p
\v 28 ꞌEnega muliyega Yesu ma ina tononoyao silugu anuwaya, ga nada taudimo. ꞌEnega tonono nidi Yesu sieonena sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, mwaꞌadega ꞌaboꞌama ga nigeya sawesawemaya be yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌaula apwese?”   
\p
\v 29 Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Nigeya ꞌebweu to yage ꞌenega be yaluyaluwa biꞌi taula apwese. Nate namo sidesidega, Yaubada ꞌenaya.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina mwawasa manuna ꞌisimana  
\r (Madiu 17:22-23; Luke 9:43-45)  
\p
\v 30 Gote ꞌenega Yesu ma ina tononoyao sena nina sipilisinena, ta Yesu geya nuwana be boda sida mwalatoni mane ꞌena sitautauya, ꞌenega Galili ꞌedana ꞌena sitauya,  
\v 31 ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌieꞌitedi ꞌina mwawasa manuna, ꞌigwae, “Maꞌetamo Tomota Natuna\f + \fr 9:31 \fk Tomota Natuna: \ft Yesu tauna ꞌieesena The Son of Man, ꞌana mwalatoi tomota tuga. Yesu taunamo ꞌieesena Tomota Natuna, ta ꞌina eꞌitao ꞌediyega tomota simwalatonina ꞌaene tauna Toꞌetoseyana Keliso. \f* ꞌana totelesipupu ꞌida ꞌebwayae ꞌana talauwalao ꞌediya be siloemwawasi, be ꞌasiyata ꞌetoi muliyega ꞌida toololimana.”  
\v 32 Ta ꞌina eꞌita gete manuna nigeya simwalamwalatoni, ta esi nigeya ꞌidi ꞌInapwana ꞌena sienaenaida, manuna simatauta.   
\s1 Tonugana taudi tomuliya  
\r (Madiu 18:1-5; Luke 9:46-48)  
\p
\v 33 ꞌEnega ꞌasa Kapaneumi ꞌena siapwesa ga anuwaya silugu, ga nada Yesu ꞌienaida ꞌina tononoyao ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “To yage manuna waegewagewana ꞌedaya?”  
\v 34 Ta siomayamaya ga nigeya sieeꞌisa, manuna ꞌidi egewagewana ꞌalena nate yaita ꞌediyega ꞌida anugana.   
\p
\v 35 \x * \xo 9:35 \xt Mk 10:43-44; Lu 22:24\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌimiyatowa ga site tuwelo ꞌibwauyedima ga ꞌieꞌita ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAbo yaita ꞌoyo nuwanuwayo be ꞌemiyega ꞌueꞌinapwana, ꞌilobwenemu be tauyo ꞌugimwaꞌuteyo be ꞌuetoguinuwa gosemwao manudi.”  
\v 36 \x * \xo 9:36 \xt Yo 13:20\x*Ta ꞌebweu gwama ꞌiꞌauꞌewenama ga gamwagamwanidiya ꞌietoolona ta ꞌiꞌatubwailina ga ꞌieonedi,  
\v 37 ꞌigwae, “ꞌEguma yaita ꞌoyo gwama gete nadigega ꞌuobobome manugu, nate ꞌaboꞌagu wate ꞌuobobomegu, ta nigeya ꞌaene taugumo ꞌuobobomegu, ta wate ꞌagu toetune Yaubada maꞌiyagu ꞌuobobomema.”   
\s1 ꞌAbo yaita tauna nigeya ꞌietaetalauwaleda tauna ꞌilemelemeda  
\r (Luke 9:49-50)  
\p
\v 38 \x * \xo 9:38 \xt Num 11:27-29\x*Ta Yoni ꞌilolagata ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌebweu tai ꞌaꞌitena ꞌamu esanega yaluyaluwa biꞌi ꞌiulaula apwesedi, ꞌenega ꞌaꞌetobodena, manuna tai nina nigeya ꞌida boda.”   
\p
\v 39 Ta Yesu esiya ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo waꞌetoꞌetobode. Manuna ꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita yage waiwaidi ꞌagu esanega ꞌiguiguinuwedi, geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu wate ꞌisinasinaligu.  
\v 40 \x * \xo 9:40 \xt Lu 11:23\x*Manuna ꞌeguma yaisigedi nigeya sietaetalauwaleda taudi silemelemeda.   
\p
\v 41 “Ta wate wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi ꞌaene ꞌeguma tonaꞌami ꞌiyapayapasa be ꞌebweu yaita ꞌienumami manuna ꞌomi Keliso ꞌina bodao, tauna ꞌana pali boboꞌana maꞌetamo ꞌiloba.   
\s1 Toꞌase ꞌigie toꞌumaliyeda  
\r (Madiu 18:6-9; Luke 17:1-2)  
\p
\v 42 “Ta esi ꞌeguma yaita ꞌitoo be ꞌagu toemisao gogama getedi ꞌediyega ꞌebweuna ꞌigie beꞌuye, tai nina nai waine nina ꞌilobwenena be gulewa sinabwana ꞌotonaya silosipwa be magulewana siula mwaꞌutedi niꞌuya.   
\p
\v 43 “Wate ꞌeguma nimayo ꞌigie beꞌuyeyo ꞌilobwenena be ꞌuꞌupwa yaule. Nate nigeya ꞌana toꞌumalinamo ꞌeguma manima ꞌupwaꞌupwayo ta yawasiyo boboꞌana ꞌuloba. Ta esi toꞌumali wawasae ꞌemuya ꞌeguma manima luwaluwayo siula mwaꞌuteyo kaiwe ꞌalaꞌalata atayana ꞌenaya.  
\v 44 (-)   
\p
\v 45 “Be wate ꞌeguma ꞌaeyo ꞌigie beꞌuyeyo ꞌilobwenena be ꞌuꞌupwa yaule. Nate nigeya ꞌana toꞌumalinamo ꞌeguma ma imu lopegoi ta yawasiyo boboꞌana ꞌuloba. Ta esi toꞌumali wawasae ꞌemuya ꞌeguma maꞌae luwaluwayo siula mwaꞌuteyo ꞌasagabugabu ꞌena.  
\v 46 (-)   
\p
\v 47 “Matayo wate nadigega, ꞌeguma ꞌigie beꞌuyeyo ꞌuꞌiwa yaule tuga, manuna nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌana toꞌumalinamo ꞌeguma mamata ꞌebweꞌebweuyo ta Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebe loina ꞌuloba. Ta esi toꞌumali wawasae ꞌemuya ꞌeguma mamata luwaluwayo siula mwaꞌuteyo ꞌasagabugabu ꞌenaya.  
\v 48 Sena nina ꞌena kokowa ꞌediya ipwaipwa sisopisopila ataya, be wate kaiwe nigeya ꞌida kweu.   
\p
\v 49 “ꞌEnega tomota maiboꞌadi ꞌawesabelulu ꞌida gieboboꞌanedi, nadigega ola masula ꞌigie boboꞌanena.   
\p
\v 50 \x * \xo 9:50 \xt Lu 14:34; Kol 4:6; 1 Te 5:13\x*“Ola yage boboꞌana. Ta ꞌeguma ꞌana lotoona ꞌisasawala, nigeya sawesawenaya be ꞌiboboꞌana limana. ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenemi be ꞌimi bubuna taumi walotoona ꞌana dibidibi nadigega waeoboobobomemi ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna ꞌenaya.”   
\c 10  
\s1 Saꞌila manuna  
\r (Madiu 19:1-12)  
\p
\v 1 Ga Yesu sena nina ꞌipilisinena ga Yudia ꞌina senaya ꞌitauya ga ꞌiabala bwasi Yolidani mali esenaya, ga boda sinabwana siegogonama ꞌenaya, ta ꞌenega ꞌina bubuna nadigega ꞌieꞌita ꞌediya.   
\p
\v 2 Ta Palisiyao simai ga nuwanuwadi be Yesu sitoo, ꞌenega ꞌena sienaida, sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, mwaꞌadega ꞌida loina saꞌila manuna? Kapekapeyana be tai mwanena ꞌisaꞌilei?”   
\p
\v 3 Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega Mosese loina ꞌiꞌebwayaꞌesemi?”   
\p
\v 4 \x * \xo 10:4 \xt 2 Loi 24:1\x*Ga Palisiyao sigwae, “Mosese ꞌitagwala be ꞌabo tai nuwanuwana be ꞌisasaꞌila, nugana pwepwai ꞌena ꞌina guitoyasa ꞌisimane be mwanena ꞌiꞌebwaꞌe ta ꞌenega ꞌisaꞌile.”   
\p
\v 5 Ga Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mosese loina nate ꞌiꞌetoladina ꞌomi ꞌimi debapaꞌala manuna.  
\v 6 \x * \xo 10:6 \xt Nug 1:27\x*Ta esi wada nuwaꞌiꞌisi Yaubada ꞌina mweluluwa ꞌunu ꞌenega tomota ꞌeluwa ꞌimweluluidi, meꞌolotona ta mewainena.  
\v 7 \x * \xo 10:7 \xt Nug 2:22-24; Ep 5:31\x*Gete ꞌalena ꞌenega tai tamana be sinana ꞌida pilisinedi be mwanena maꞌiyana simiyaluwa,  
\v 8 be siteluwa nidi oodi ꞌebweuna tuga. Lowa siteluwa nidi simiya dumaduma ta gete tuga niꞌatu sieꞌebweu.  
\v 9 Yaubada niꞌatu ꞌisaꞌu luwedi ꞌenega geyaꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita ꞌiemiya dumedumedi.”   
\p
\v 10 ꞌEnega muliyega Yesu ma ina tononoyao siilama anuwaya ga tonono nidi sienaida limana saꞌila manuna.  
\v 11 \x * \xo 10:11 \xt 1 Ko 7:10-11\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, “ꞌEguma yaita tai mwanena ꞌisaꞌile be ꞌiaibala mali waine ꞌena, tai gete gimimwanena ꞌena ꞌiguinuwa toꞌumalina, manuna ꞌiloelata.  
\v 12 Ta wate ꞌeguma waine mwanena ꞌisaꞌile be ꞌiaibala mali tai ꞌena, waine nina ꞌiloelata.”   
\s1 Yesu gogama ꞌiona obobomedi  
\r (Madiu 19:13-15; Luke 18:15-17)  
\p
\v 13 Ta ꞌenega tomota gogama simeꞌedi Yesu ꞌenaya be ꞌaene ꞌida gitoodi. Ta ꞌina tononoyao esi gogama nidi siꞌetobodedi.  
\v 14 \x * \xo 10:14 \xt Md 18:2-3\x*Ta Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌiꞌitedi ga ꞌienapaꞌaledi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo gogama waꞌetoꞌetobodedi, ta esi wada tagwaledi be ꞌeguya sida mai, manuna gogama getedi nadigega Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌilobwene ꞌaiꞌailidi.  
\v 15 Manuna ꞌabo yaisigedi taudi geyaꞌabo gogama getedi nadigega ꞌidi emisa, geyaꞌabo saꞌi Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌena silugulugu.”   
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega Yesu gogama nidi ꞌiꞌaalidi ta ꞌigitoodi ga ꞌiona obobomedi.   
\s1 Esaesa manuna  
\r (Madiu 19:16-30; Luke 18:18-30)  
\p
\v 17 Ga Yesu ꞌitoolo be ꞌaene ꞌitatauya, ta ꞌebweu tai ꞌipilima ga ꞌiꞌaetulasa Yesu matanaya ta ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, yamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌoyo toeꞌita boboꞌana, ꞌenega toꞌase yada guinuwe be ꞌenega yawasigu ataya yaloba?”   
\p
\v 18 Ga Yesu tai nina ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega ga ꞌenega ꞌuꞌawa boboꞌanegu? Manuna nigeya ꞌebweu yaita boboꞌana; nate namo Yaubada.  
\v 19 \x * \xo 10:19 \xt Sia 20:12-17\x*Ta Yaubada ꞌina loinao niꞌatu ꞌumwalamwalatonidi, nate ꞌaene:  
\p Geyaꞌabo loemwawasa.  
\p Geyaꞌabo loelata.  
\p Geyaꞌabo ꞌipwala.  
\p Geyaꞌabo simana kabokabo.  
\p Geyaꞌabo kaboega tomota ꞌidi gwegwe ꞌuꞌewaꞌewadi.  
\p Ta wate tamayo be sinayo ꞌuda ꞌamayabedi.”   
\p
\v 20 Ga tai nina ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌigu tuta gwamega ga batuwa loina nidi getedi yamuliya ꞌaiꞌailedi.”   
\p
\v 21 \x * \xo 10:21 \xt Mk 8:34\x*\x * \xo 10:21 \xt Mk 4:18-19\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ma ina gwausowala tai nina ꞌiduneyena ta ꞌigwae, “Nate namo ꞌebweuna yage ꞌilogegesemu. ꞌEnega ꞌuila ꞌimu ꞌasaya be ꞌimu gwegwe maiboꞌadi ꞌuegimwaneyedi be ꞌadi maisa ꞌueguyaiyedi togomabeso ꞌediya, ta ꞌenega ꞌumamai be ꞌumuliyegu, be ꞌenega maꞌetamo ꞌimu esaesa galewaya ꞌuda loba.”   
\p
\v 22 Ona gete tai nina ꞌinonona ta ꞌina esaesa sinabwana ꞌiegagalena, ꞌenega nuwana ꞌimwau ꞌaiꞌaila, ta ꞌiila.   
\p
\v 23 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌiloꞌita dadana ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAbo yaisigedi ma idi esaesa sinabwana ꞌidi lugu Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina solanaya mwauna.”   
\p
\v 24 Ta ꞌina tononoyao nuwadi ꞌiowana ꞌina ona gete manuna. ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Natugwao, Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌana lugu mwau wawasae.  
\v 25 Onaꞌaiꞌaila kameli tauna yobai sinabwana, ꞌenega tupwana mwauna be siyaluma ꞌana lobwalena ꞌenega ꞌilulugu, ta esi toesaesao ꞌidi lugu Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌenaya mwau wawasae.”   
\p
\v 26 Yesu ꞌina ona gete manuna ꞌina tononoyao sinuwa owana wawasae ga sieonena, “ꞌEguma gete nadigega, yaita sana sawesawenaya be ꞌebe gwausowala ꞌiloba?”   
\p
\v 27 \x * \xo 10:27 \xt Lu 1:37\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌiduneyedi ga ꞌigwae, “Yage gete mwau wawasae tomota ꞌediya, ta esi nigeya mwauna Yaubada ꞌenaya, manuna Yaubada ꞌenaya yage maiboꞌana kapekapeyana.”   
\p
\v 28 \x * \xo 10:28 \xt Mk 1:16-20; Lu 5:28\x*ꞌEnega Pita ꞌilolagata ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌaboꞌama mwaꞌadega? Manuna ꞌima gwegweyao maiboꞌadi niꞌatu ꞌapilisinedi ta ꞌamuliyemu.”   
\p
\v 29 Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌeguma yaisigedi ꞌomi ꞌimi anuwao, tasimiyao, nuumiyao, sinamiyao, tamamiyao, natumiyao be ꞌimi bwaꞌao wate wapilisinedi, ta wate ꞌelouya wada loba manugu be tetela boboꞌana ꞌana simana manuna,  
\v 30 ꞌami eꞌisa gete tuga wada loba nadigega analedi anuwao, tasimiyao, nuumiyao, sinamiyao, natumiyao be ꞌimi bwaꞌao, ta wate maꞌetamo galewaya yawasimi ataya waloba.  
\v 31 Ta gete tuga toanuganao yaudi maꞌetamo sida muliya be taudi simulimuliya maꞌetamo sida nugana.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina mwawasa ꞌana simana ꞌetonina  
\r (Madiu 20:17-19; Luke 18:31-34)  
\p
\v 32 \x * \xo 10:32 \xt Mk 8:31, 9:31\x*ꞌEnega maꞌetamo ꞌedaya situꞌetuꞌe Yelusalema manuna, ga Yesu ꞌinuganugana ta ꞌina tononoyao simulimuliya, be ma idi nuwaowana, ta ꞌaina tomota wate ma idi matauta ꞌedaya simulimuliyedi. ꞌEnega ꞌina tononoyao site tuwelo nidi ꞌibwau egogona limedi ga ꞌiemataluwedi toꞌase ꞌiabe ꞌiapwesa ꞌenaya,  
\v 33 ꞌigwae, “Gete tuga tatuꞌetuꞌe Yelusalema. ꞌAboꞌagu Tomota Natuna ta ꞌagu tosipupu nina ꞌida telesipupuyegu totaliyao sinabwadi be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌediya, be ꞌigu mwawasa manuna sida loina, be muliyega sida ꞌebwayaegu taudi nigeya me Yudia ꞌediya,  
\v 34 be sida tuyeyegu be sigiwaligu be balaeyega sisapigu be ꞌenega siloemwawasigu, be ꞌasiyata ꞌetoi yatoolo limana.”   
\s1 Yemesa be Yoni ꞌidi sida Yesu ꞌena  
\r (Madiu 20:20-28)  
\p
\v 35 ꞌEnega Yemesa be Yoni, taudi Sebedi natunao, Yesu ꞌena simai ga sieonena, sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌamai sabi sida ꞌemuya.”   
\p
\v 36 Ga Yesu ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase nuwanuwami be yada guinuwa manumi?”   
\p
\v 37 Ta sigwae, “Maꞌetamo ꞌimu ꞌebeloina ꞌena nuwanuwama be selabemuya ꞌada miyatowa, ꞌebweu ꞌataimuya ta ꞌebweu gegeumimuya.”   
\p
\v 38 \x * \xo 10:38 \xt Mk 14:36\x*Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌOmi ꞌimi sida gete ꞌana mwalatoi nigeya wamwalamwalatoni. Mwaꞌadega ꞌelouya keigana ꞌenega yanunuma, kapekapeyana be ꞌomi wate ꞌenega wanunuma? Ta wate bapitaiso mwauna nina maꞌetamo yaloba, mwaꞌadega ꞌomi wate nadigega sawesawemiya be wada bapitaisoꞌesa?”   
\p
\v 39 \x * \xo 10:39 \xt Gu 12:2; Et 1:9\x*ꞌEnega sigwae, “Sawesawemaya.” Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila, keiga nina ꞌenega yanunuma ꞌomi wate ꞌenega wanunuma, be wate bapitaiso nina ꞌenega ꞌiabe yada bapitaiso ꞌomi wate ꞌenega wada bapitaiso,  
\v 40 ta esi nigeya sawesaweguya be yaesinuwa yaisigedi maꞌetamo ꞌigu etoloina ꞌenaya ꞌataiguya be gegeumiguya sida miyatowa, manuna Yaubada tauna ꞌina ꞌebeloina be ꞌiesinuwa.”   
\p
\v 41 Ta tononoyao site sanau Yemesa be Yoni ꞌidi sida sinonona ga sigamwasowaledi.  
\v 42 ꞌEnega Yesu maiboꞌadi ꞌibwau egogonedima ga ꞌieonedi, “ꞌOmi wamwalatonina taudi baleꞌuya sieesedi ꞌaene ꞌinapwanao ꞌidi tomotaiyao siloiloina paꞌaledi.  
\v 43 \x * \xo 10:43 \xt Mk 9:35\x*Ta ꞌomi geyaꞌabo wate nadigega taudi waguiguinuwaꞌesa. Ta ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo nuwanuwayo be ꞌemiyega ꞌuetoloina ꞌilobwenemu be gosemwao manudi ꞌuda etoguinuwa.  
\v 44 Ta wate ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo nuwanuwayo be ꞌemiyega ꞌuetoanugana, ꞌilobwenemu be gosemwao maiboꞌadi manudi ꞌuetopaisewa.   
\p
\v 45 \x * \xo 10:45 \xt 1 Ti 2:5-6\x*“Ta ꞌaboꞌagu Tomota Natuna\f + \fr 10:45 \fk Tomota Natuna: \ft Yesu tauna ꞌieesena The Son of Man, ꞌana mwalatoi tomota tuga. Yesu taunamo ꞌieesena Tomota Natuna, ta ꞌinaꞌitao eꞌediyega tomota simwalatonina ꞌaene tauna Toꞌetoseyana lKeiso. \f* yamai baleꞌuya nigeya ꞌaene tomota manugu siguinuwa, ta esi sabi guinuwa tomota manudi, ta wate yatagwalegu be yamwamwawasa tomota maiboꞌami ꞌami etoliꞌama manuna.”   
\s1 Batimio matana ꞌiꞌesasedi  
\r (Madiu 20:29-34; Luke 18:35-43)  
\p
\v 46 ꞌEnega simai Yeliko ꞌena, ga tuta nina Yesu ma ina tononoyao Yeliko sipilisinena, boda sinabwana siꞌoayabudi, ga tomata kebokebo ꞌana esana Batimio silobena, tauna Timio natuna, ta tuta yauna ꞌeda tupitupinaya ꞌimiyami ta ꞌiesidasida mani be gwegwe manudi.   
\p
\v 47 \x * \xo 10:47 \xt Md 9:27\x*Ga Batimio nina ale ꞌinonona ꞌaene Yesu goma Nasaleta ꞌitautauya, ꞌenega Yesu ꞌena ꞌibwau, ꞌigwae, “Yesu ye, ꞌoyo Debida ꞌina susu, ꞌuda ꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyegu!”   
\p
\v 48 ꞌEnega tomota maiboꞌadi Batimio nina siꞌetobodena, sigwae, “Ulosaꞌu! Tuwa bwau!” Ta tuga ꞌibwau toitoila, ꞌigwae, “Debida tubuna ye, ꞌuda ꞌatenuwa ꞌoleꞌoleyegu.”   
\p
\v 49 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌitoolo, ta ꞌiona, “Wada bwauyenama.” Ga tomota sigwae, “Boboꞌana, ꞌutoolo. Yesu ꞌibwauyemu.”   
\p
\v 50 ꞌEnega ꞌana talaꞌapwala ꞌiꞌewa yaulena ga ꞌitoolo manini, ga Yesu ꞌena ꞌimai.   
\p
\v 51 Ta Yesu ꞌieonena ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase nuwanuwayo be manuyo yada guinuwe?” Ga tomata kebokebo nina ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, kapekapeyana be matagu ꞌuda gieꞌesasedi?”   
\p
\v 52 \x * \xo 10:52 \xt Mk 5:34\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “Boboꞌana! Gete tuga ꞌimu emisa ꞌenega matayo ꞌiꞌesasedi niꞌatu.” Gote ꞌena matana ꞌiꞌesasedi, ga ꞌedaya Yesu ꞌimuliyena.   
\c 11  
\s1 Yesu ꞌina lugu Yelusalema ꞌena  
\r (Madiu 21:1-11; Luke 19:28-40; Yoni 12:12-19)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega situꞌetuꞌe Yelusalema manuna ga ꞌasa gidalidi Betani ta Betipegi selabediya silogelogedo, nate ꞌoya Olibe ꞌagalaunaya, ta Yelusalema nuganidiya tupwana ꞌedasola. ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌeluwa ꞌigimi etunedi sena nidi gidalidi ꞌediya ma ꞌadi emataluwa,  
\v 2 ꞌigwae, “Watauya ꞌasa gote matamiya ꞌenaya, ta ꞌeguma waapwesa ꞌasa nina matanaya, yobai ꞌebweu waꞌitaloba kaiwe ꞌena silosipwena, nate ase mwaneyauna, tauna nigeya tomota sida gelu toona. Yobai nina waliꞌami be wameꞌe.  
\v 3 Ta ꞌabo ꞌebweu yaita ꞌienaida ꞌemiya be ꞌigwae, ‘Toꞌase manuna nate yobai nina waliꞌaliꞌami?’ tai nina waeona, ‘ꞌInapwana nuwanuwana, be tuta kukupana namo be ꞌida etune ilenama.’ ”   
\p
\v 4 ꞌEnega site luwa nidi sitauya ꞌasa nina ꞌenaya ga yobai ase silobena anuwa mataꞌawaninaya, ta kaiwe ꞌena silosipwena, ꞌenega sieꞌale be siliꞌami.  
\v 5 Siliꞌaliꞌami ta ꞌaina tomota sitootoolo selabediya sigwae, “Toꞌase manuna nate yobai nina waliꞌaliꞌami?”   
\p
\v 6 Ta site luwa nidi sigwae, “ꞌInapwana nuwanuwana, be tuta kukupana namo be ꞌida etune ilenama,” ga ꞌediya sitagwalena.  
\v 7 Ta yobai nina siꞌewena ga sitauyena Yesu ꞌena, ga ꞌadi ꞌoamega gwauna siloesona, ꞌenega Yesu ꞌigelutuꞌe, ga ꞌitautauya.   
\p
\v 8 Ta boda yaudi wate ꞌadi ꞌoamao ꞌedaya siesodi, ta ꞌaidi kaiwe nalidi mayawadi siguledi ꞌeda ꞌana eiyala manuna.   
\p
\v 9 \x * \xo 11:9 \xt Sam 118:25-26\x*Ta ꞌaina boda Yesu sianuganena ta ꞌaina boda siamuliya, ga maiboꞌadi silotuputupu ta sibwaubwau, sigwae, “Kamatoki ꞌInapwana, Yaubada ꞌana esanega ꞌumai sabi ꞌetoseyema.  
\v 10 ꞌEbeloina tubumao Debida ꞌenega ꞌiapwesa limanama. Gete manuna Yaubada Toloetana sana ꞌatuputupu.”   
\p
\v 11 Ga Yesu niꞌatu Yelusalema ꞌena ꞌiapwesa ga Anuwa Tabu ꞌena ꞌilugu, ga yage yauna Anuwa Tabu solanaya ꞌiduneyedi, ta niꞌatu ꞌasuinuwanuwa, ꞌenega ma ina tononoyao site tuwelo siila Betani ga nada siꞌeno.   
\s1 Yesu kaiwe ꞌebweu ꞌibaꞌena  
\r (Madiu 21:18-19)  
\p
\v 12 Ga tomwa ꞌiulisina ga sitoolo ga Betaniyega siilaila limana Yelusalema manuna, ta Yesu ꞌibotana,  
\v 13 ga ꞌedasolega kaiwe ꞌana ꞌita ꞌatuwa damaya mayawana ꞌiꞌitena, ꞌenega ꞌinao selabenaya be nuwanuwana ꞌaene uwanega ꞌida loepaꞌala, ta esi ꞌiꞌitena yawa daisinamo, tuga ꞌaweuwauwa maꞌetamo ꞌadi tuta.  
\v 14 \x * \xo 11:14 \xt Mk 11:20\x*ꞌEnega Yesu kaiwe nina ꞌibaꞌena ga ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo wate ꞌuuwauwa limana be tomota ꞌenega siꞌeꞌai.” Ga ꞌina ona gete ꞌina tononoyao sinonona.   
\s1 Yesu togimwane ꞌipaꞌidi Anuwa Tabu solanega  
\r (Madiu 21:12-17; Luke 19:45-48; Yoni 2:13-22)  
\p
\v 15 ꞌEnega Yelusalema ꞌena simai, ga Anuwa Tabu solanaya ꞌilugu, ga toegimwaneyao be togimwaneyao solanega ꞌipaꞌi apwesedi, ta mani ꞌana toesaꞌugelasao ꞌidi tebeli ꞌiꞌaubuiyedi, ta bunebune ꞌadi toegimwaneyao ꞌidi ꞌebemiya wate ꞌiꞌaubuiyedi.  
\v 16 Ta wate anuwa solana ꞌiegagalena be geyaꞌabo tomota ma idi gwegwe sitautauya anuwa solanega.  
\v 17 \x * \xo 11:17 \xt Ais 56:7\x*Ga ꞌieꞌitedi ꞌigwae, “Nai Buki Tabu ꞌena Yaubada ꞌina ona siꞌetoladina wamwalatonina, ꞌigwae, ‘ꞌIgu anuwa sida eese anuwa ꞌebe sidasida tomota maiboꞌadi manudi,’ ta ꞌomi wagibunina ga ꞌaene ꞌimi ꞌebe ꞌipwala.”   
\p
\v 18 \x * \xo 11:18 \xt Mk 14:1\x*Ta totaliyao sinabwadi be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao Yesu ꞌina guinuwa gete tetelina sinonona, ꞌenega sigamwasowalena ga sinuwa edaedadama be sida loemwawasi, ta nigeya sawesawediya, manuna simatautena, ta wate Yesu ꞌina eꞌitao tomota yauyaudi nuwadi ꞌiꞌewena.   
\p
\v 19 Ga niꞌatu ꞌiboi, ꞌenega Yesu ma ina tononoyao ꞌasa nina siebesinena.   
\s1 Kaiwe nina Yesu ꞌibaꞌebaꞌena ꞌiꞌoapelu  
\r (Madiu 21:20-22)  
\p
\v 20 \x * \xo 11:20 \xt Mk 11:14\x*Ta tomwa ꞌiulisina ga sitoolo sabi ila Yelusalema, ga ꞌedaya sitautauya, ta Yesu kaiwe nina ꞌibaꞌebaꞌenaya siꞌitena niꞌatu yawana maiboꞌana siꞌoapelu.  
\v 21 ꞌEnega Pita Yesu ꞌina ona ꞌinuwaꞌiꞌisina ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌuꞌita kaiwe nina ꞌubaꞌebaꞌenaya niꞌatu ꞌiꞌoapelu.”   
\p
\v 22 Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEguma ꞌimi emisa wasaꞌu Yaubada ꞌena, ꞌomi wate ꞌimi guinuwa waiwaidi wada guinuwedi.  
\v 23 \x * \xo 11:23 \xt Lu 17:6\x*Wate yaona ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌemiya ꞌeguma yaita ꞌoyo nigeya ꞌuda enuwanaluwa ta esi ꞌuemiemisa be toꞌase ꞌuda ona sida apwesa tuga, ꞌeguma ꞌoya gote ꞌuloine be ꞌugwae, ‘ꞌUmiya dolo olaya,’ ꞌimu ona ꞌida ematamatane tuga.   
\p
\v 24 \x * \xo 11:24 \xt Md 7:7; Yo 14:13-14\x*“ꞌEnega yaeonami toꞌase waside Yaubada ꞌena, wada emisa tuga be maꞌetamo wada loba.  
\v 25 \x * \xo 11:25 \xt Md 6:14-15\x*Wate ꞌabo wasidasida Yaubada ꞌena, gosemiyao ꞌidi loegesiyao wanuwataudi ꞌabo toꞌase ꞌidi bubuna ꞌemiya, be gete ꞌenega Tamami galewaya ꞌomi wate ꞌimi loegesiyao ꞌida nuwataudi.”  
\v 26 (-)   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina loina manuna  
\r (Madiu 21:23-27; Luke 20:1-8)  
\p
\v 27 ꞌEnega niꞌatu siilama Yelusalema, ta Yesu Anuwa Tabu solanaya ꞌiadadana, ga totaliyao be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao be wate ꞌinapwanao simai,  
\v 28 \x * \xo 11:28 \xt Yo 2:18\x*ga Yesu sienaidena, sigwae, “Tai, yaita ꞌina loinega ga gete nadigega ꞌuguiguinuwaꞌesa?”   
\p
\v 29 Ga Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Nugana yagimi enaida ꞌemiya be ꞌeguma waeꞌisa, ꞌaboꞌagu wate yaeonami ꞌigu loina manuna.  
\v 30 ꞌIgu enaida gete: Yaita ꞌina loinega ga Yoni togiebapitaiso ꞌiguiguinuwa? Yaubada, nai ꞌebweu tomota?”   
\p
\v 31 ꞌEnega taudimo ꞌediya siegewagewana, sigwae, “ꞌIna ona mwaꞌadega taeꞌisaꞌese? Manuna ꞌabo tagwae, ‘Yaubada ꞌenega,’ ꞌiabe ꞌieona limada be ꞌigwae, ‘Ta! Toꞌase sana manuna ga Yoni nigeya waemiemise?’  
\v 32 \x * \xo 11:32 \xt Md 21:46\x*Ta ꞌeguma tagwae, ‘Tomota ꞌenega,’ ꞌiabe pwalu sigamwasowaleda.” Manuna tomota yaudi Yoni siemisena ꞌaene tauna palopita ꞌaiꞌaila.  
\v 33 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌina enaida nigeya sieꞌieꞌisa ꞌaiꞌaili, ta esi sigwae, “Nigeya ꞌamwalamwalatoni.”  
\p Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu geyaꞌabo wate ꞌemiya yasimasimana apwesa yaita ꞌina loinega ga gete nadigega yaguiguinuwaꞌesa.”   
\c 12  
\s1 ꞌInapwana ꞌina bagula ꞌana topaisewao  
\r (Madiu 21:33-46; Luke 20:9-19)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌiona semalimaliyedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEbweu tai ꞌina bagula ꞌiasona oine daisinamo ga ꞌali ꞌiguinuwena, ga oine ꞌana ꞌebebibi ꞌiguinuwena ga anuwa bagula solanaya ꞌiꞌabina, ꞌenega ꞌina toguinuwao ꞌiloinedi be siꞌitaꞌiꞌisi, ta tauna ꞌitauya mali esenaya.   
\p
\v 2 “Ta sesoi ꞌana tutaya, ꞌinapwana nina ꞌina ꞌaliꞌei ꞌebweuna ꞌietunena be ꞌaene oine uwana bagula ꞌana toꞌitaꞌiꞌitao ꞌediyega ꞌida meꞌedi.  
\v 3 ꞌItautauya ga nigeya siꞌebwaꞌebwaꞌe, ta esi sigiyaina ga sisapina ꞌenega maꞌanimenimenamo sietunena ga ꞌiila.   
\p
\v 4 “ꞌEnega ꞌinapwana nina ꞌina ꞌaliꞌei ꞌeluwena wate ꞌietunena ꞌediya, ga siununa debanaya ga ma ina omayamaya ꞌiila.   
\p
\v 5 “Ta wate ꞌetonina ꞌietunena ꞌediya ga siloemwawasina. Ta yaudi wate ꞌietunedi ꞌediya ga ꞌaidi sisapidi ta ꞌaidi siloemwawasidi, ga ꞌenega maiboꞌadi sigie toꞌumaliyedi.   
\p
\v 6 “Gote ꞌena ꞌebweuna namo ꞌimiyami, tauna natuꞌaiꞌailina. ꞌEnega tauna wate ꞌietunena ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, ‘Tauna sana natugu, ꞌenega sida ꞌamayabe.’   
\p
\v 7 “Ta niꞌatu natuna ꞌiapwesa ꞌediya ga toꞌitaꞌiꞌitao nidi taudimo ꞌediya sigwae, ‘Gosemao, ꞌInapwana gete natuna ꞌimeemai, ꞌenega batuwa nina taloemwawasi be ꞌaboꞌada bagula taloine.’  
\v 8 \x * \xo 12:8 \xt Ib 13:12\x*Ta sigiyaina ga siloemwawasina ga bagula ꞌetaulunaya siula apwesena.”   
\p
\v 9 Ga niꞌatu Yesu ꞌina emwasala ꞌigumwala, ga ꞌienaida ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase ꞌiabe ꞌinapwana nina ꞌiguinuwe? Onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌinapwana nina ꞌimama be toguinuwa nidi ꞌiloemwawasidi, be ꞌenega bagula nina mali toꞌitaꞌiꞌitao ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi.”   
\p
\v 10 \x * \xo 12:10 \xt Sam 118:22-23; 1 Pi 2:6-8\x*ꞌEnega Yesu wate onasemalimali Buki Tabu ꞌenega ꞌisimanena, ꞌigwae, “Wanuwaꞌiꞌisi Buki Tabu ꞌina simana gete nadigega:  
\p ‘ꞌOla nina lowa toꞌabi anuwa siguitoyasena.  
\p Ta gete tugai niꞌatu sietoolona be ꞌieꞌola nugana,  
\p be ꞌola maiboꞌadi ꞌiloinedi.   
\p
\v 11 Nate ꞌInapwana ꞌina guinuwa ꞌebe nuwaowana ꞌedaya.’ ”   
\p
\v 12 Yesu ꞌina onasemalimali gete totaliyao sinabwadi be Palisiyao sinonona ga simwalatonina ꞌaene taudi tuga manudi ꞌionaona, ꞌenega ꞌaina ꞌedaꞌeda siꞌebesena be sida giyai, ta esi nigeya sigiyagiyai manuna simatauta pwalu ꞌediya. ꞌEnega sipilisinena ga sitauya.   
\s1 Sisa ꞌina takisi  
\r (Madiu 22:15-22; Luke 20:20-26)  
\p
\v 13 Ta ꞌenega ꞌinapwanao nidi ꞌaina Palisiyao be wate Elodi ꞌina bodao sietunedi Yesu ꞌenaya be enaidega sikaboe be ꞌina loegesi siloba.   
\p
\v 14 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌena simai ga sieonena, sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, niꞌatu ꞌamwalatonimu ꞌaene ꞌoyo toeꞌita ꞌaiꞌaila, ta tomota ꞌidi waiwai manuna nigeya ꞌumatamatauta, ta tuga ona ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌusimana leleleya tomota maiboꞌadi ꞌediya, nate Yaubada ꞌina ꞌeda ꞌueꞌita ꞌaiꞌaila. ꞌEnega mwaꞌadega? Sawesawenaya be Kini Sisa manuna takisi tasaꞌu, nai nigeya?  
\v 15 Takisi nina taemaisi Kini ꞌenaya, nai nigeya?”  
\p Ta Yesu ꞌidi kabo niꞌatu ꞌimwalatonina, ꞌenega ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase manuna watootoogu? Abaga mani nina wameꞌe be yaꞌita.”   
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega mani ꞌebweuna siꞌebwaꞌena. Ga Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Wada eonagu, mani gete ꞌena yaita ꞌana maꞌamaꞌyau ta ꞌana esana?”  
\p Ta sigwae, “Kini Sisa.”   
\p
\v 17 \x * \xo 12:17 \xt Lo 13:7\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, “O nadigega. ꞌEnega ꞌeguma Kini ꞌina yage waꞌebwaya Kini ꞌenaya, ta ꞌeguma Yaubada ꞌina yage Yaubada waꞌebwaꞌe.”  
\p Ga Yesu ꞌina ona gete manuna nuwadi ꞌiowana sinabwana.   
\s1 Tomwawasa ꞌidi toololimana  
\r (Madiu 22:23-33; Luke 20:27-40)  
\p
\v 18 \x * \xo 12:18 \xt Gu 23:8\x*ꞌEnega wate Sadusiyao, taudi nigeya siemiemisa tomwawasa ꞌidi toololimana manuna, simai ga Yesu ꞌena sienaida, sigwae,  
\v 19 \x * \xo 12:19 \xt 2 Loi 25:5\x*“ꞌInapwana, loina gete nadigega Mosese ꞌiꞌetoladina manuda, ꞌigwae, ‘ꞌAbo ꞌebweu tai ꞌiai be nigeya natunamo ta ꞌimwamwawasa, tai nina tasina kwabulinana maꞌiyana sida ai, be ꞌenega ꞌabo waine ꞌienatuna, natunao tokwaiya nina ꞌana lopaꞌeluyao.’ ”  
\v 20 ꞌEnega ꞌebeꞌita siꞌebwaꞌena, sigwae, “ꞌEbweu tai matasinao simiyami ꞌadi yau site sebeni, ga ꞌadi tomatuwa nina ꞌiai ga nigeya natunamo ta tai nina ꞌimwawasa. ꞌEnega wate tasina selabenega kwabula nina ꞌiaina ga wate nadigega nigeya natunamo ta ꞌimwawasa.  
\v 21 ꞌEnega tasina selabenega kwabula nina ꞌiꞌewena ga wate simiyamiyana ta nigeya natunamo, ta tai nina ꞌimwawasa.  
\v 22 Ta nadigega tuga tasinao maiboꞌadi kwabula nina siaiai ta simwawamwawasa, ta nigeya wate natudimo. Ta muliyega waine wate ꞌimwawasa.  
\v 23 ꞌEnega toololimana ꞌana tutaya waine nina to tai batu mwane ꞌaiꞌailina? Manuna site sebeni nidi niꞌatu siaina.”   
\p
\v 24 Ta Yesu enaida gete ꞌieꞌisena, ꞌigwae, “Gete ꞌimi loegesi, manuna Buki Tabu nigeya wamwalamwalatoni, ta wate Yaubada ꞌina waiwai nigeya wamwalamwalatoni.  
\v 25 Toololimana mulinaya tomota geyaꞌabo siaiai, ta esi ꞌidi miya aneloseyao galewaya nadigega.   
\p
\v 26 \x * \xo 12:26 \xt Sia 3:2-6\x*“Lowaenei Yaubada Mosese ꞌieonena toololimana manuna, ꞌabo Buki Tabu wasawai wada ꞌitaloba. Manuna tuta nina Mosese mitawaya ꞌitautauya ta Yaubada kaiwe sabelulu ꞌenega Mosese nina ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, ‘ꞌAboꞌagu Ebelaamo ꞌina Yaubada ta Aisake ꞌina Yaubada ta Yekobe ꞌina Yaubada.’  
\v 27 Yaubada nigeya tomota mwawamwawasidi ꞌidi Yaubada, ta esi tomota mayawasidi ꞌidi Yaubada. Ta ꞌomi ꞌimi eꞌita yage gete manuna nigeya palupaluna.”   
\s1 Loina sinabwadi  
\r (Madiu 22:34-40; Luke 10:25-28)  
\p
\v 28 ꞌEnega loina ꞌana toeꞌita ꞌebweu ꞌimai ga taudi ꞌidi egewagewana Yesu maꞌedi ꞌinonona ga ꞌidi enaidao ꞌadi eꞌisa Yesu ꞌenega ꞌinonodi boboꞌana wawasae, ꞌenega tauna wate Yesu ꞌena ꞌienaida, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, loinao maiboꞌadi ꞌediyega to loina sinabwana?”   
\p
\v 29 \x * \xo 12:29 \xt 2 Loi 6:5\x*Ta ꞌenega Yesu ꞌigwae, “Loina sinabwana gete: ꞌOmi me Isileli ꞌigu ona gete wanonoi ꞌaene ꞌInapwana Yaubada tebweuna namo,  
\v 30 ꞌenega ꞌimu ꞌInapwana Yaubada ꞌuda obobome ꞌateyo be yaluyaluwayo be nuwayo be wate ꞌimu waiwai maiboꞌana ꞌediyega.   
\p
\v 31 \x * \xo 12:31 \xt 1 Loi 19:18; Lo 13:9-10; Ga 5:14\x*“Ta ꞌebweu wate loina sinabwana gete: Gosemwao ꞌuda obobomedi, nadigega tauyo ꞌamu oboboma.  
\p “Loina ꞌeluwa getedi loina maiboꞌadi sisinabwa sinedi.”   
\p
\v 32 ꞌEnega loina ꞌana toeꞌita nina Yesu ꞌina ona ꞌinonona ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, ꞌimu ona nate ona ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌaene tauna tebweuna tuga Yaubada, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate Yaubada ꞌimiyami.  
\v 33 \x * \xo 12:33 \xt Osi 6:6\x*ꞌEnega ꞌilobweneda be taobobome ꞌateda maiboꞌanega be nuwada maiboꞌanega be ꞌida waiwai maiboꞌanega, be wate gosedao tada obobomedi nadigega tauda taobobomeda. Loina ꞌeluwa getedi taliya yauyaudi be ꞌebwayadaitao maiboꞌadi sisinabwa sinedi, aga?”   
\p
\v 34 Ta Yesu tai nina ꞌina ona ꞌinonona ꞌaene palupaluna, ga ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, “Nate ona ꞌaiꞌaila, ta ꞌoyo Yaubada ꞌina ꞌebeloina ꞌena niꞌatu ꞌuloselabena.”  
\p ꞌEnega muliyega tomota Yesu simatautena ga nigeya ꞌebweu yaita ꞌitootoo be ꞌienaida limana ꞌenaya.   
\s1 Toꞌetoseyana nina tauna Debida ꞌina susu  
\r (Madiu 22:41-46; Luke 20:41-44)  
\p
\v 35 Ta ꞌenega Yesu Anuwa Tabu solanaya ꞌieꞌieꞌita tomota ꞌediya, ga ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega ga ꞌenega ꞌaina loina ꞌana toeꞌitao sigwae ꞌaene Debida ꞌina susuyega Toꞌetoseyana Keliso ꞌiapwesa,  
\v 36 \x * \xo 12:36 \xt Sam 110:1; Gu 2:34-35\x*manuna lowa Yaluyaluwa Tabuna Debida ꞌigiesinapuna ga Debida Toꞌetoseyana nina ꞌiꞌawa ꞌinapwanena, ꞌigwae:  
\p Yaubada ꞌiona ꞌigu ꞌInapwana ꞌenaya, ꞌigwae,  
\p “ꞌAtaiguya ꞌumiyatowa be ꞌana laba  
\p ꞌamu talauwalao yasaꞌu mwaꞌutedi ꞌaeyo ꞌubuninaya.”   
\p
\v 37 Debida nina ꞌina ꞌInapwana Keliso, ꞌenega mwaꞌadega sana ga Debida ꞌina susuyega muliyega Keliso ꞌiapwesama?”  
\p Ta boda maiboꞌadi Yesu ꞌina eꞌita nuwadi ꞌiꞌewena.   
\s1 Yesu loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌiꞌawa toꞌumaliyedi  
\r (Madiu 23:1-36; Luke 20:45-47)  
\p
\v 38 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo loina ꞌana toeꞌitao ꞌidi bubuna wamulimuliye. Manuna taudi adelidi tuga nadigega tuta yauna nuwanuwadi be ꞌadi ꞌoamao duduladi siꞌotedi be tomota gamwagamwanidiya sisakosakowasi be ꞌaene sida ꞌamayabedi.  
\v 39 Ta wate nuwanuwadi ꞌebemiya boboꞌadi Anuwa Tapwalolo ꞌediya, be wate sagali ꞌadi tutaya nuwanuwadi be bwaimaya sida miyatowa.  
\v 40 Ta wate tuta yauna tomota matadiya Yaubada ꞌena sisidasida dudulana, ta esi ꞌidi sida nina nigeya boboꞌana, manuna ꞌatediya sinuwanuwa mwaꞌadega ꞌiabe kwabulao sikaboꞌesedi be ꞌidi gwegweyao siꞌewadi. ꞌEnega maꞌetamo Yaubada eꞌisa toꞌumalina ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi.”   
\s1 Kwabula ꞌina ꞌebwayadaita  
\r (Luke 21:1-4)  
\p
\v 41 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌebwayadaita ꞌana ꞌebesaꞌu deinaya ꞌimiyatowa, ga tomota yaudi ꞌidi ꞌebwayadaita mani sisaꞌusaꞌu ta Yesu ꞌiyoꞌoyoꞌo, ga toesaesao ꞌidi ꞌebwayadaita sinabwadi ꞌiꞌitedi,  
\v 42 ta wate kwabula gomagomabesona ꞌiꞌitena ꞌina ꞌebwayadaita toea ꞌeluwa namo ꞌisaꞌudi.   
\p
\v 43 \x * \xo 12:43 \xt 2 Ko 8:12\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌibwau egogonedima, ga ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila, kwabula gote ꞌina ꞌebwayadaita maiboꞌadi ꞌidi ꞌebwayadaita ꞌisinabwa sinedi.  
\v 44 Manuna maiboꞌadi ꞌidi tupwa sinabwana ꞌimiyami, ta esi kwabula gote gomagomabesona ta ꞌina mani maiboꞌana ꞌisaꞌuna, ga nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌina tupwa ꞌimiyami be ꞌenega ꞌana masula ꞌida gimwane.”   
\c 13  
\s1 Tuta mwauna maꞌetamo ꞌiapwesama  
\r (Madiu 24:1-14; Luke 21:5-19)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega Yesu ma ina tononoyao Anuwa Tabu ꞌenega siapwesa, ga ꞌina tonono ꞌebweu Anuwa Tabu ꞌana anuwao Yesu ꞌena ꞌieꞌitaena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana ꞌuꞌita anuwa getedi ꞌadi guinuwa boboꞌana wawasae, gulewa sinabwadi ꞌediyega siꞌabidi.”   
\p
\v 2 \x * \xo 13:2 \xt Lu 19:44\x*Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Anuwa nidi sinabwadi ꞌuꞌitaꞌitadi maꞌetamo maiboꞌadi siligeya yauledi be geyaꞌabo wate ꞌebweu tupwa waꞌitaꞌita lima.”   
\p
\v 3 Muliyega Yesu ꞌitauya Olibe ꞌoyana ꞌena ga ꞌimiyatowaya ta ꞌenega Anuwa Tabu Yelusalema ꞌenaya ꞌidunedune, ga Pita, Yemesa, Yoni be Anidulu simai ga taudimo Yesu maꞌedi, ꞌenega sieonena, sigwae,  
\v 4 “ꞌInapwana, ꞌueonama to tuta ꞌena Anuwa Tabu nidi siligeidi ta to weꞌiweꞌiyaya ꞌadi ꞌita ꞌediyega ꞌada mwalatoni ꞌaene yage nidi ꞌuonaediya ꞌiabe siapwesama?”   
\p
\v 5 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌilolagata ga ꞌediya ꞌigwae, “Waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi ꞌabona nai tomota ꞌaidi sikaboemi.  
\v 6 \x * \xo 13:6 \xt Mk 13:21-22; 1 Yo 2:18\x*Manuna maꞌetamo tomota yaudi ꞌagu esanega simama be ꞌaene sianugana gesiyemi, be ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna ꞌida gwae, ‘ꞌAboꞌagu Toꞌetoseyana nina,’ be tomota yaudi sida muliyedi.  
\v 7 Wate ale ꞌetamo wanonodi saiyao selabemiya ta ꞌedasolaya manudi, ta geyaꞌabo waꞌateꞌate saꞌala, manuna yage getedi sida apwesa nugana ta esi baleꞌu ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa ꞌana tuta maꞌetamo.  
\v 8 Manuna ꞌetamo mali boda mali boda ꞌediya sida losaiya, ta wate mali ꞌebeloina mali ꞌebeloina ꞌediya sida losaiya, be wate mwaniꞌiniꞌi siapwesa sena yaudi ꞌediya, be botana sinabwadi sida apwesa. Ta yage getedi tuta mwaudi ꞌana ꞌebe eꞌale tuga.   
\p
\v 9 \x * \xo 13:9 \xt Md 10:17-22\x*“Ta ꞌomi esi waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi, manuna tomota sida giyaimi be sitauyemi etala manuna, be Anuwa Tapwalolo ꞌediya ꞌetamo sisapisapimi, ta wate ꞌiabe toloinao be kiniyao matadiya siꞌauꞌewami be watoolo ta sietalaemi, manuna ꞌomi ꞌaene ꞌigu bodao, be teteligu ꞌediya wada simane.  
\v 10 \x * \xo 13:10 \xt Md 28:19\x*Ta tetela boboꞌana ꞌida ꞌelelewana nugana sena maiboꞌana ꞌediya be muliyega tuta ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa ꞌida apwesa.   
\p
\v 11 “Ta ꞌabo toloinao matadiya sietoolomi sabi etala, geyaꞌabo waꞌateꞌate saꞌala be ꞌaene wada onaꞌesa, ta esi ma imi ꞌatepatu wada ona tuga, manuna nigeya ꞌomi ꞌimi ona wasimasimane, ta esiya Yaluyaluwa Tabuna tuta gote ꞌena ona ꞌiꞌebwaꞌemi be wasimana apwese.   
\p
\v 12 “Ta wate tuta simeemai ꞌediya tomota ꞌidi susu solanaya losaiya ꞌida apwesa manugu, nate tai tasina ꞌisipupuyei be siloemwawasi. Be nadigega wate tamana natuna ꞌida sipupuyei be siloemwawasi. Be wate gogama sinadiyao be tamadiyao sida etalauwaledi be siloemwawasidi.  
\v 13 \x * \xo 13:13 \xt Yo 15:18-21\x*Be tomota maiboꞌadi sida etalauwalemi manuna ꞌomi ꞌaene ꞌagu toemisao. Ta ꞌabo yaita ꞌieꞌalamaꞌiꞌita be ꞌitoolopaꞌala be ꞌana laba tuta ꞌana ꞌebe losalowa ꞌenaya, gwausowala ataya ꞌida loba.   
\s1 Mwau sinabwana  
\r (Madiu 24:15-28; Luke 21:20-24)  
\p
\v 14 \x * \xo 13:14 \xt Dan 11:31\x*“Maꞌetamo ꞌeguma tomota waꞌita yage toꞌumali wawasae ta gadilulu sietoolo sena etaetabuna ꞌena (ꞌAbo yaita ona gete ꞌisawai ꞌida nuwa sabwalena), tuta gote ꞌenaya Yudia ꞌana tomiyanao ꞌilobwenedi be ꞌoya ꞌediya sidedena.  
\v 15 Ta ꞌeguma yaita bwaimaya ꞌimiyami ꞌida dena manini ta geyaꞌabo ꞌilugulugu limana ꞌina anuwaya ꞌina gwegwe sabi ꞌewadi.  
\v 16 Be ꞌabo yaita bagulaya ꞌipaipaisewa geyaꞌabo ꞌiilaila ꞌana ꞌoama mali esenaya ꞌisaꞌunaya manuna.   
\p
\v 17 “Ta tuta gote ꞌenaya toꞌeuwanao be toesusuyao sienuwaꞌoleꞌole.  
\v 18 ꞌEnega wada sidasida be tuta boboꞌana Yaubada ꞌida ꞌebwaꞌemi ꞌimi tuta dena ꞌenaya, ta geyaꞌabo gogai ꞌana tutaya.   
\p
\v 19 \x * \xo 13:19 \xt Dan 12:1\x*“Onaꞌaiꞌaila tuta gote mwau wawasae, manuna tuta nina Yaubada baleꞌu ꞌimweluluina ꞌenega ga batuwa nigeya ꞌebweu wate mwau gete nadigega, ta muliyega mwau gete geyaꞌabo wate ꞌiapwesapwesa limana.  
\v 20 Mwau gote ꞌana ꞌasiyatao ꞌeguma Yaubada geyaꞌabo ꞌigiegie kukupai ꞌiabe tomota maiboꞌadi simwamwawasa, ta esi Yaubada ꞌasiyata nidi ꞌida giekukupa, nate tauna ꞌina tomotai esiesinuwadi manudi.   
\p
\v 21 “ꞌEnega ꞌabo yaita ꞌieonami be ꞌigwae, ‘Keliso gete’ nai ‘Gote’ geyaꞌabo waeemisedi.  
\v 22 \x * \xo 13:22 \xt 2 Te 2:9; Et 13:13\x*Manuna Keliso kabokabo be palopitao kabokabo ꞌiabe siapwesa be weꞌiweꞌiyaya waiwaidi tomota ꞌediya sida eꞌitaedi, be ꞌediyega ꞌabo sawesawediya Yaubada ꞌina bodao esiesinuwadi sikwakwani.  
\v 23 ꞌEnega waꞌitaꞌiꞌisimi manuna yage getedi manudi niꞌatu yagimi simanedi ꞌemiya.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina ila limanama  
\r (Madiu 24:29-31; Luke 21:25-28)  
\p
\v 24 \x * \xo 13:24 \xt 2 Pi 3:10; Et 6:12-13\x*“Ta tuta mwau nina ꞌigugumwala be muliyega sinala ꞌiguguyoi be wate nawalae ꞌina maedana ꞌikwekweu,  
\v 25 be kwadimao galewega sibebeꞌu, be yage yauyaudi galewaya simiyami ꞌidi waiwai sida neneta.  
\v 26 \x * \xo 13:26 \xt Md 26:64\x*ꞌAboꞌagu Tomota Natuna, be tuta gote me baleꞌu maiboꞌadi siꞌitagu pwanega yamwaꞌumwaꞌutama ma igu waiwai ta ma igu esaesa sinabwana,  
\v 27 \x * \xo 13:27 \xt 1 Te 4:16-17\x*be ꞌenega ꞌigu aneloseyao yaetunedi be ꞌigu boda esiesinuwadi siegogonedima baleꞌu be galewa be yagila maiboꞌadi ꞌidi senao ꞌediyega.   
\s1 ꞌEbeꞌita saido ꞌenega  
\r (Madiu 24:32-35; Luke 21:29-33)  
\p
\v 28 “ꞌEbe ꞌita saido ꞌenega yada eꞌitami ꞌaene ꞌeguma saido\f + \fr 13:28 \fk saido: \ft ꞌEbeꞌita gete me Yudia ꞌidi kaiwe ꞌana esana pigi (fig), uwana tupwana nadigega damaya uwana, ta esi yawadi sisagusagu nadigega saido.\f* yawadi auwaudi ꞌigalugalu wamwalatonina ꞌaene losiye ꞌana tuta ꞌiloseloselabe.  
\v 29 Ta wate weꞌiweꞌiyaya nidi niꞌatu ꞌemiya yasimanedi, ꞌeguma to tuta waꞌitalobadi niꞌatu wamwalamwalatoni ꞌaene ꞌigu tuta ila limanama niꞌatu ꞌiloseloselabena.  
\v 30 Onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌepata gete geyaꞌabo wagumwagumwala be ꞌana laba yage nidi maiboꞌadi sida apwesa.   
\p
\v 31 “Maꞌetamo galewa ta baleꞌu sisasawala ta ꞌigu onao geyaꞌabo saꞌi sisawasawala.   
\s1 ꞌIna mai ꞌana tuta nigeya mwalatoninamo  
\r (Madiu 24:36-44)  
\p
\v 32 \x * \xo 13:32 \xt Gu 1:7\x*“Nigeya ꞌebweu yaita ꞌimwalamwalatoni to tuta nai to ꞌasiyata ꞌena yaila limanama, ta wate aneloseyao galewaya nigeya simwalamwalatoni. ꞌAboꞌagu wate nigeya yamwalamwalatoni. Ta Tamagu tebweuna namo ꞌimwalamwalatoni.  
\v 33 \x * \xo 13:33 \xt Md 25:13\x*ꞌEnega walomataꞌiꞌita manuna ꞌigu tuta ila limanama nigeya wamwalamwalatoni.”   
\p
\v 34 ꞌEbeꞌita wate Yesu ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌEguma ꞌebweu ꞌinapwana ꞌiabe ꞌina anuwa ꞌida pilisine be ꞌitatauya mali senaya, ꞌina toguinuwao ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna ꞌidi paisewa ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi, be ꞌiloinedi be ꞌaene ꞌina anuwa siꞌitaꞌiꞌisi, ta wate anuwa ꞌana ꞌawa ꞌana toꞌitaꞌiꞌita ꞌieonena, ꞌigwae, ‘Geyaꞌabo ꞌuꞌenoꞌeno ta esi ꞌulomataꞌiꞌita ꞌaiꞌaila.’  
\v 35 \x * \xo 13:35 \xt Lu 12:37-38\x*ꞌEnega ꞌilobwenemi be walomataꞌiꞌita be wayamwayamwagu, manuna toni anuwa ꞌina mai ꞌana tuta nigeya wamwalamwalatoni, nai ꞌasuinuwanuwaya, nai niuniuwanaya, nai tomwa uliulitaya, nai gonagonaya.  
\v 36 Ta geyaꞌabo yalatuma be ꞌenoꞌenoega yaloeloesalutuimi.   
\p
\v 37 “ꞌIgu emataluwa gete ꞌomi ꞌemiya be wate tomota maiboꞌadi ꞌediya ꞌaene wada lomataꞌiꞌita ꞌaiꞌaila.”   
\c 14  
\s1 ꞌInapwanao nuwanuwadi be Yesu siloemwawasi  
\r (Madiu 26:1-5; Luke 22:1-2; Yoni 11:45-53)  
\p
\v 1 \x * \xo 14:1 \xt Sia 12:1-27; Mk 10:33-34\x*Ataona Sagalina ꞌana ꞌebe nuwaꞌiꞌita ꞌida apwesa ꞌasiyata ꞌeluwa mulidiya. Sagali nina ꞌenaya pwalawa daisina, nigeya ꞌana ꞌebe gieseseyamo, siꞌaꞌani. Ta totaliyao sinabwadi be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao sinuwanuwa edaedadama mwaꞌadega Yesu sida kaboꞌese be ꞌaene sida giyai be sida loemwawasi,  
\v 2 ta sigwae, “Geyaꞌabo sagali solanaya Yesu tagiyagiyai ꞌabona nai tomota sigamwasowaleda be silosaiya ꞌedaya.”   
\s1 Waine Yesu ꞌieoloina ꞌasa Betani ꞌenaya  
\r (Madiu 26:6-13; Yoni 12:1-8)  
\p
\v 3 Tuta nina Yesu Betani ꞌena ꞌimiyami, ta ꞌiꞌeꞌai Saimoni ꞌina anuwaya, tauna lowa tolepelo ꞌebweu; ga waine ꞌebweu ma ina bunama ꞌiluguma; ta bunama nina ꞌana esana nadi, ꞌana maisa sinabwana, ta ꞌana botolo boboꞌana wawasae ꞌenaya ꞌisiwena. Ta waine botolo ꞌawana ꞌiꞌaulasena ga bunama nina Yesu debanaya ꞌisiwena.   
\p
\v 4 Ta ꞌaina tomota siꞌitena ga waine silomugiyena, sigwae, “Toꞌase manuna bunama ꞌimudalina?  
\v 5 ꞌIlobwenena be bunama nina ꞌigimwaneye be ꞌana maisa ꞌetoi analedi kina nadigega ꞌiꞌewa be ꞌieguyaiye togomabeso ꞌediya.” ꞌEnega waine nina siꞌena paꞌalina.   
\p
\v 6 Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Tuwa! Walosaꞌu! Geyaꞌabo waine wagie dededoni, manuna ꞌina lema gete ꞌeguya boboꞌana wawasae.  
\v 7 Togomabeso nidi waoneonedi tuta maiboꞌana selabemiya simiyami, be ꞌabo to tuta nuwanuwami wada lemedi, ta ꞌaboꞌagu esi nigeya tuta dudulana maꞌemi tamiyami.  
\v 8 \x * \xo 14:8 \xt Yo 19:40\x*Ta waine gete toꞌase sinabwana nadigega ꞌenaya ꞌiguinuwena ꞌeguya, nate bwalagu ꞌigimi eoloina sabi gibubu ꞌagu saꞌuꞌaliꞌali manuna.  
\v 9 Ta onaꞌaiꞌaila, maꞌetamo teteligu ꞌana loguguya tomota sinoonoi baleꞌu maiboꞌana ꞌenaya, ta waine gete ꞌina guinuwa ꞌeguya tetelina sida emwasali wate.”   
\s1 Yudasa ꞌina tagwala Yesu ꞌana telesipupu manuna  
\r (Madiu 26:14-16; Luke 22:3-6)  
\p
\v 10 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌina tonono ꞌebweu site tuwelo ꞌediyega, tauna Yudasa Isikaliota, ꞌitauya totaliya sinabwadi ꞌediya ga nuwanuwana be Yesu ꞌediya ꞌida telesipupuye.  
\v 11 Ga Yudasa ꞌina ona sinonona ga sigwausowala ga ꞌena siona upaupa be ꞌaene ꞌana maisa siꞌebwaꞌe. ꞌEnega Yudasa tuta boboꞌana ꞌiyamwena be ꞌaene Yesu ꞌediya ꞌida telesipupuye be sigiyai.   
\s1 Yesu ma ina tononoyao siꞌeꞌai  
\r (Madiu 26:17-25; Luke 22:7-14, 21-23; Yoni 13:21-30)  
\p
\v 12 \x * \xo 14:12 \xt Sia 12:14-20\x*Ataona Sagalina solanaya beledi daisina nigeya gieseseinamo sieꞌani ga sagali ꞌana ꞌasiyata nugana ꞌena lamiyao siunudi Ataona ꞌana ꞌebe nuwaꞌiꞌita manuna, ga ꞌasiyata nina ꞌena Yesu ꞌina tononoyao sieonena, sigwae, “ꞌInapwana, mane ꞌena nuwanuwayo be Ataona Sagalina manuyo ꞌagibubu?”   
\p
\v 13 ꞌEnega ꞌina tononoyao ꞌeluwa ꞌietunedi ta ꞌieonedi, “Watatauya Yelusalema, be ꞌabo tai ꞌebweuna ma ina ꞌebe gobwasi ꞌiꞌaalina waloba, tai nina wamuli ꞌoayabu  
\v 14 be maꞌemi walulugu anuwaya, be toni anuwa waeona, wagwae, ‘ꞌIma toeꞌita gete nadigega ꞌionaꞌesa, “To sena ꞌutagwale be ꞌena ma igu tononoyao Ataona masulina ꞌaꞌaꞌani?” ’  
\v 15 Be ꞌenega ꞌiabe sena sinabwana etanaya gibugibubuna ꞌieꞌitami, tauna ꞌena Ataona masulina wagibubu manuda.”   
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega tonono nidi sitauya ga ꞌasa Yelusalema ꞌena silugu ga toꞌase nadigega Yesu ꞌisimanena ꞌediya yage nidi maiboꞌadi silobedi, ga anuwa nina ꞌena Ataona masulina sigibubuna manudi.   
\p
\v 17 Ta ꞌasuinuwanuwaya Yesu ma ina tononoyao simai  
\v 18 \x * \xo 14:18 \xt Sam 41:9\x*ga site tuwelo simiyatowa sabi ꞌeꞌai. Ta ꞌidi ꞌeꞌai solanaya Yesu ꞌieonedi, “Gosegwao yaona ꞌaiꞌaila ꞌaene ꞌebweuna tai gete tuga maꞌedai taꞌeꞌai, ta saꞌi ꞌiabe ꞌitelesipupuyegu.”   
\p
\v 19 Ta Yesu ꞌina ona gete manuna sinuwa mwau, ga ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna Yesu ꞌena ꞌienaida, ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, yaita? Nai ꞌaboꞌagu?”   
\p
\v 20 Ga Yesu ꞌigwae, “ꞌAgu tosipupu nina ꞌomi wate tuwelo ꞌemiyega, ta tauna maꞌiyagu gaeba ꞌebweuna ꞌenega ꞌaꞌeꞌai.  
\v 21 ꞌAboꞌagu Tomota Natuna maꞌetamo yatatauya ꞌeda nina lowa Buki Tabu ꞌena ꞌigimisimanena, ta esi ꞌagu totelesipupu nina nuwaꞌoleꞌolena saꞌi; ta boboꞌana ꞌabo lowa sinana geyaꞌabo ꞌida enaenatune, manuna ꞌina tubuwa ꞌenega ꞌienuwaꞌoleꞌole ꞌina guinuwa toꞌumalina manuna.”   
\s1 ꞌInapwana ꞌina ꞌeꞌai  
\r (Madiu 26:26-30; Luke 22:15-20; 1 Kolinita 11:23-25)  
\p
\v 22 ꞌEtamo siꞌeꞌai ta Yesu masula ꞌiꞌewena ga manuna ꞌiona oboboma ta ꞌigitomwena ga ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi, ꞌigwae, “Gete waꞌewa oogu.”   
\p
\v 23 Ta oine makeigana wate ꞌiꞌewena ga manuna ꞌilokagutoki Yaubada ꞌena ga ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi, ga maiboꞌadi sinuma.  
\v 24 \x * \xo 14:24 \xt Sia 24:8; 1 Ko 10:16; Yo 6:54-56\x*Ta wate ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Gete lalagu ꞌidaudau tomota yaumi manumi, nate loina auwauna.  
\v 25 Ta yaeonemi tuta gete be mulinaya oine gete geyaꞌabo ꞌenega yanumanuma limana ga ꞌana laba oine auwauna yanunuma Yaubada ꞌina senaya.”   
\p
\v 26 ꞌEnega wali ꞌebweuna siwaliyena ta siapwesa ga situꞌe ꞌOya Olibe ꞌenaya.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌisimana apwesa eyaseyase manuna  
\r (Madiu 26:31-35; Luke 22:31-34; Yoni 13:36-38)  
\p
\v 27 \x * \xo 14:27 \xt Yo 16:32; Sak 13:7\x*Ta Yesu ꞌieonedi, “ꞌIabe maiboꞌami wada denasinegu, nadigega Buki Tabu ꞌina simana, ꞌigwae,  
\p ‘Toꞌitaꞌiꞌita sipi yaloemwawasi be sipi nidi sida ꞌelelewana.’   
\p
\v 28 \x * \xo 14:28 \xt Mk 16:7\x*Ta ꞌigu toololimana mulinaya Galili ꞌena yatatauya be ꞌomi muliguyega wawawai.”   
\p
\v 29 ꞌEnega Pita ꞌilolagata ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌIabe maiboꞌadi sidena sineyo ta tebweugu maꞌiyayo.”   
\p
\v 30 \x * \xo 14:30 \xt Mk 14:66-72\x*Ta Yesu Pita ꞌieonena, “Yaona ꞌaiꞌaila, boiboi batuwa muliyega be kakaleko ꞌigwagwane maluwa, ta ꞌoyo ꞌuda gimi eyaseyaseyegu matoi.”   
\p
\v 31 Ta ꞌenega Pita ma ina ꞌawapaꞌala ꞌigwae, “ꞌInapwana, geyaꞌabo saꞌi yaeyaseyaseyeyo. ꞌEguma siloemwawasiyo ꞌaboꞌagu wate maꞌiyayo siloemwawasida.” Tononoyao maiboꞌadi wate nadigega sionaꞌesa.   
\s1 Yesu Gedesemane ꞌena ꞌisidasida  
\r (Madiu 26:36-46; Luke 22:39-46)  
\p
\v 32 Ga sitauya ꞌebweu sena ꞌana esana Gedesemane ꞌena, ga ꞌina tononoyao ꞌediya ꞌigwae, “Gete ꞌena wamiyami, ta ꞌaboꞌagu yasisida Yaubada ꞌena.”  
\v 33 Ta site toi maꞌenao ꞌiꞌauꞌewedi, taudi Pita be Yemesa be Yoni, ꞌenega Yesu ma ina ꞌateuyauya ta ma ina nuwamwau,  
\v 34 \x * \xo 14:34 \xt Yo 12:27\x*\x * \xo 14:34 \xt Ib 5:7-8\x*ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAtegu ꞌiuyauya sinabwana nai ꞌiabe yamwamwawasa, ꞌenega bada wamiyami ta walomataꞌiꞌita.”   
\p
\v 35 Ta Yesu ꞌialaga tupwana ga ꞌibeꞌu sanamwaꞌuta ga ꞌisidasida ꞌaene ꞌabo kapekapeyana ꞌelouya gete Yaubada ꞌida ꞌewayaule,  
\v 36 \x * \xo 14:36 \xt Yo 6:38\x*ꞌigwaegwae, “Tamagu ye, guinuwa yauna sawesawemuya, ꞌenega nuwanuwagu be ꞌelouya keigana gete ꞌeguyega ꞌuꞌewayaule, ta geyaꞌabo ꞌaboꞌagu ꞌigu nuwena ꞌenega ta ꞌoyo esi ꞌimu nuwena ꞌenega ꞌuda guinuwa.”   
\p
\v 37 ꞌEnega ꞌiila ga site toi nidi ꞌilobedi niꞌatu siꞌeno mwataya, ga Pita ꞌiloanoanona, ꞌigwae, “Saimoni, mwaꞌadega ꞌuꞌenoꞌeno. Nigeya sawesawemuya be tuta gidalina namo manuna ꞌumata paꞌala, aga?”   
\p
\v 38 Ga wate ꞌieonedi maiboꞌadi, ꞌigwae, “ꞌIlobwenemi be wamata paꞌala be wasidasida be ꞌenega geyaꞌabo Seitani ꞌitootoomi. Onaꞌaiꞌaila, yaluyaluwami nuwanuwana ta tuga manuna oomi sitaba.”   
\p
\v 39 ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌilaga limana ta ꞌina sidasida niꞌa ꞌilolimena.   
\p
\v 40 Ta Yesu wate ꞌiila ꞌina tononoyao ꞌediya ga ꞌilobedi wate siꞌeno mwataya, manuna matadi niꞌatu siꞌenoꞌeno. Ta ꞌiloanoanodi ga sitoolo ma idi omayamaya, ga nigeya ꞌidi ꞌebe onamo.   
\p
\v 41 Ga Yesu wate ꞌilaga ga ꞌisidasida, ta ꞌina ilama ꞌetonina ꞌenaya ꞌilobedi siꞌeno mwataya, ga ꞌieonedi, “Mwaꞌadega, maꞌetamo tuga waꞌenoꞌeno ta waeyawaiꞌata, aga? Ta waꞌita, ꞌaboꞌagu Tomota Natuna ꞌigu tuta niꞌatu ꞌiapwesa be sida sipupuyegu totoꞌumalidi ꞌediya.  
\v 42 Watoolo be tatatauya, manuna ꞌagu totelesipupu nina niꞌatu gete ꞌimeema.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌana giyaina  
\r (Madiu 26:47-56; Luke 22:47-53; Yoni 18:2-12)  
\p
\v 43 Yesu ꞌetamo ꞌionaona ga Yudasa ꞌiapwesama, tauna Yesu ꞌina tononoyao site tuwelo ꞌebweuna ꞌediyega. Ta wate totaliya sinabwadi be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao be ꞌinapwanao tolosaiyao Yudasa maꞌedi sietunedi be ꞌaene Yesu sida giyai, ta boda nidi ma idi sisisaiyao be wepasiyao wate simeꞌedi.   
\p
\v 44 Ta Yudasa weꞌiweꞌiyaya niꞌatu ꞌediya ꞌisimanena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAbo yaita yaꞌatubwaili, nate tauna Yesu, be wagiyai ta walomataꞌiꞌisi be watauye.”  
\v 45 ꞌEnega ꞌitauya palupaluna Yesu ꞌena ga ꞌilokagutokiyena ta ꞌiꞌatubwailina.  
\v 46 ꞌEnega boda nidi siapwesama ga Yesu sigiyaina.   
\p
\v 47 Ta Yesu ꞌina bodao ꞌebweuna ꞌediyega ꞌitootoolo selabenaya ga ꞌina sisisaiya ꞌilisilolona ga totaliya sinabwana ꞌina toguinuwa tenana ꞌiꞌupwa yaulena.   
\p
\v 48 \x * \xo 14:48 \xt Yo 18:20\x*Ta Yesu boda ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Sana ꞌaboꞌagu toꞌipwala ga ꞌenega ma imi sisisaiya be ma imi wepasi wamai sabi giyaigu.  
\v 49 Ta toꞌase ꞌalena ga ꞌenega nigeya wagiyagiyaigu ꞌasiyata nidi yaudi gamwagamwanimiya yamiyami Anuwa Tabu ꞌena ta yaeꞌieꞌita tomota ꞌediya? Ta tuwa tuga yage getedi siapwesama be ꞌaene palopitao ꞌidi gimisimana Buki Tabu solanaya sida apwesa.”   
\p
\v 50 \x * \xo 14:50 \xt Md 26:31; Yo 16:32\x*ꞌEnega Yesu ꞌina tononoyao maiboꞌadi sidena sinena.  
\v 51 Ta ꞌebweu tubuwau ma ꞌana ꞌoama ꞌebweuna namo Yesu ꞌiꞌoayabuna, ta tolosaiyao nuwanuwadi sigiyai,  
\v 52 ta sigisaꞌilina ga ꞌana ꞌoamamo siꞌewena, ta mabubugewana ꞌidena.   
\s1 Yesu siꞌauꞌewena toloinao ꞌediya  
\r (Madiu 26:57-68; Luke 22:54-55, 63-71; Yoni 18:13-14, 19-24)  
\p
\v 53 Ta Yesu siꞌauꞌewena ga siluguyena totaliyao ꞌidi ꞌinapwana ꞌina anuwaya, manuna anuwa nina ꞌena totaliya sinabwadi be ꞌinapwanao be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao niꞌatu siegogonama ga simiyami.  
\v 54 Ta Pita ꞌedasolega Yesu ꞌimuliyena ga ꞌimai totaliya sinabwana nina ꞌina ꞌasaya, ga Pita nina toꞌitaꞌiꞌitao maꞌediya simiyatowa, ta kaiwe ꞌena sisiyasiyata.   
\p
\v 55 ꞌEnega totaliya sinabwadi be ꞌinapwanao nidi nuwanuwadi Yesu ꞌana toeꞌewao sida lobadi be ꞌidi eꞌewa ꞌenega Yesu sida loemwawasi, ta nigeya ꞌebweu wate silobaloba.  
\v 56 Manuna toeꞌewa yaudi sisimasimana, ta esi ꞌidi simana nigeya leleleya. Taudi maiboꞌadi tokabo tuga.  
\v 57 \x * \xo 14:57 \xt Yo 2:19-21\x*Ta ꞌaidi ꞌediyega sitoolo ga Yesu sieꞌewa kabokaboena, sigwae,  
\v 58 “Yesu ꞌina ona ꞌebweu ꞌanononaya, ꞌigwae, ‘Anuwa Tabu gete tomota siꞌabinaya maꞌetamo yalige yaulei be ꞌasiyata ꞌetoi ꞌediya yada ꞌabilima, ta nigeya tomota nimadiyega.’ ”  
\v 59 Ta saꞌi ꞌidi simanao yage gete manuna nigeya sieleleleya.   
\p
\v 60 ꞌEnega totaliya sinabwana nina matadiya ꞌitoolo ga Yesu ꞌienaidena, ꞌigwae, “Nigeya ꞌimu eꞌisamo, aga? Tomota gotedi ꞌidi eꞌewa ꞌemuya niꞌatu ꞌunononaya?”  
\v 61 \x * \xo 14:61 \xt Mk 15:5; Ais 53:7\x*Ta Yesu tuga ꞌiꞌalaenono, ga nigeya ꞌionaona.  
\p Ta ꞌenega totaliya sinabwana Yesu ꞌena ꞌienaida limana, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega ꞌoyo Yaubada natuna Toꞌetoseyana niyo, nai nigeya?”   
\p
\v 62 \x * \xo 14:62 \xt Mk 13:26; Dan 7:13\x*Ga Yesu ꞌigwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu tauna, Tomota Natuna nigu, be maꞌetamo waꞌitagu Toewaiwai sana ꞌatainaya yamiyami be wate galewa pwananao debadiyega yamama.”   
\p
\v 63-64 \x * \xo 14:63-64 \xt Yo 19:7; 1 Loi 24:16\x*ꞌEnega totaliya sinabwana nina ꞌigamwasowala ꞌaiꞌaila, ꞌenega taunamo ꞌana ꞌoama ꞌisabuna ta ꞌigwae, “ꞌIna ona toꞌumalina wanononaya? Onaꞌaiꞌaila tai gete Yaubada ꞌisinalina. Tuwa! Geyaꞌabo wate ꞌana toeꞌewao sionaona ꞌina loegesiyao manudi. Mwaꞌadega ꞌimi nuwanuwa Yesu manuna?”  
\p Ta ꞌenega maiboꞌadi silolagata ga sigwae, “ꞌIlobwenena be ꞌimwamwawasa!”   
\p
\v 65 \x * \xo 14:65 \xt Ais 53:5\x*Gote ꞌena ꞌaina tomota Yesu sigiwalina, ga matana ꞌoamega siwaduna ta siunu dadanena ma idi ꞌeetete, sigwae, “ꞌUeonama yaita ꞌisapimu.”  
\p Ta toꞌitaꞌiꞌitao nidi Yesu sigiyaina ga sisapisapi ta sitautauye.   
\p
\v 66 Ta Pita maꞌetamo ꞌetauluya ꞌimiyami, ga totaliya sinabwana ꞌina toguinuwa gomagweine ꞌebweuna ꞌiapwesama,  
\v 67 ga Pita ꞌiꞌitena ꞌisiyasiyata. ꞌEnega waine nina Pita ꞌiduneduneye ga ꞌigwae, “ꞌOyo goma Nasaleta Yesu nina lowa maꞌiyayo wamiyami, aga?”   
\p
\v 68 Ta Pita ꞌieyaseyase, ꞌigwae, “Yage nina ꞌuonaonae nigeya yamwalamwalatoni.” ꞌEnega Pita ꞌidena ga tupwana ꞌiaapwesa.   
\p
\v 69 Ta gomagweine nina Pita ꞌienima susuyena tomiya nidi ꞌediya, ꞌigwae, “Tai gote Yesu ꞌina boda ꞌebweu.”   
\p
\v 70 Ga Pita ꞌinonona ga ꞌieyaseyase limana, ꞌigwae, “ꞌAboꞌagu nigeya.”  
\p Tuta kukupana namo mulinaya toyoꞌo nidi Pita sieonena, sigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila ꞌukabo. ꞌOyo Yesu ꞌina boda ꞌebweu, manuna ꞌoyo goma Galili.”   
\p
\v 71 ꞌEnega Pita ꞌisawatamatamana ta ona toꞌumalina ꞌenega ꞌibwautuꞌe, ꞌigwae, “Yesu tauna manuna waonaona, ꞌaboꞌagu nigeya wate yamwalamwalatoni. Tamada!”  
\v 72 \x * \xo 14:72 \xt Mk 14:30\x*Ta tuta gote ꞌena kakaleko ꞌigwane ꞌeluwena, ga Pita ꞌinuwaꞌiꞌisina Yesu ꞌina ona ꞌaene “Muliyega be kakaleko ꞌigwagwane maluwa, ta ꞌoyo ꞌuda gimi eyaseyaseyegu matoi.” Ta ꞌenega Pita ꞌina kabo toꞌumalina ꞌinuwaꞌiꞌisina ga ꞌidedoi.   
\c 15  
\s1 Yesu ꞌina etala Pailato matanaya  
\r (Madiu 27:1-2, 11-14; Luke 23:1-5; Yoni 18:28-38)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega tomwa ꞌiulisina ga totaliyao sinabwadi be ꞌinapwanao be loina ꞌadi toeꞌitao be toloinao maiboꞌadi sideli egogonama ga siloiloina Yesu manuna, ꞌenega nimana siyonidi ga sitauyena Pailato ꞌena be ꞌaene Pailato nina ꞌida loine.   
\p
\v 2 ꞌEnega Pailato Yesu ꞌienaidena, ꞌigwae, “ꞌUda simana, ꞌoyo me Yudia ꞌidi kini, aga?”  
\p Ta Yesu ꞌigwae, “Niꞌatu nate ꞌuona saba.”   
\p
\v 3 Ta ꞌenega totaliyao sinabwadi yage yaudi manudi Yesu sieꞌewena.  
\v 4 ꞌEnega Pailato Yesu ꞌienaida limena, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega nigeya ꞌimu eꞌisamo? Simana getedi ꞌamu eꞌewa manuna ꞌunononaya?”   
\p
\v 5 \x * \xo 15:5 \xt Mk 14:61; Ais 53:7\x*Ta Yesu nigeya ꞌebweu wate ꞌieꞌieꞌisa, ꞌenega Pailato nuwana ꞌiowana sinabwana.   
\s1 Siloina be Yesu ꞌida mwawasa  
\r (Madiu 27:15-26; Luke 23:13-25; Yoni 18:38–19:16)  
\p
\v 6 Yakwala ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna Ataona Sagalina ꞌana tuta ꞌenaya toloina nina ꞌina bubuna nate deliyega ꞌebweu tai ꞌiliꞌami be ꞌiapwesa, ꞌeguma yaita pwalu siesinuwe.   
\p
\v 7 Tuta gote ꞌena ꞌaina me Loma ꞌadi talauwalao deliya simiyami, manuna geya nuwadi me Loma ꞌidi loina ga silosaiyedi, ga ꞌebweuna ꞌediyega ꞌana esana Balaba, losaiya nina solanaya tomota ꞌiloemwawasidi. ꞌEnega me Loma Balaba magosenao sigiyaidi ga deliya sisaꞌudi.   
\p
\v 8 ꞌEnega boda siegogonama ga siꞌawanoi Pailato ꞌenaya, sigwae, “Sawesawenaya be ꞌebweu tai ꞌuda liꞌami manuma, nadigega ꞌima sidasida ꞌemuya ꞌuguiguinuwe yakwala ꞌebweuna ꞌebweuna ꞌenaya?”   
\p
\v 9 ꞌEnega Pailato ꞌieonedi, “Nuwanuwami ꞌaene me Yudia ꞌimi kini yada ꞌetoliꞌami manumi, aga?”  
\v 10 \x * \xo 15:10 \xt Yo 11:47-48, 12:19\x*Manuna Pailato ꞌimwalatonina ꞌaene totaliya sinabwadi ꞌidi eꞌipiꞌipiyega Yesu siwasegigiyena sabi loemwawasina.   
\p
\v 11 \x * \xo 15:11 \xt Gu 3:14\x*Ta saꞌi totaliya sinabwadi niꞌatu tomota nuwanuwa toꞌumalina sienuwa saꞌuyena ꞌediya, ꞌenega Yesu siguitoyasena ta Balaba esiya ꞌana esana siꞌinanena be ꞌida liꞌami manudi.   
\p
\v 12 Ta Pailato ꞌieonedi wate ꞌigwae, “Ta mwaꞌadega yada loinaꞌesa tauna waeesena ꞌimi kini?”   
\p
\v 13 Ga wate sibwau, sigwae, “Kelose ꞌena tada tutuepaꞌiye!”   
\p
\v 14 Ta Pailato ꞌigwae, “Toꞌase sana ꞌina loegesi ga ꞌenega ꞌaene mwawasa ꞌiloba?”  
\p Ta sibwau toitoila, sigwae, “Kelose ꞌena tada tutuepaꞌiye.”   
\p
\v 15 ꞌEnega Pailato nuwanuwana be pwalu ꞌida giegwausowalidi ga Balaba ꞌiliꞌamina, ta wate ꞌina tolosaiyao ꞌiloinedi be Yesu balaeyega sida sapi be muliyega sida tutuepaꞌiye kelose ꞌenaya.   
\s1 Tolosaiyao Yesu situyeyena  
\r (Madiu 27:27-31; Yoni 19:2-3)  
\p
\v 16 ꞌEnega Pailato ꞌina tolosaiyao Yesu sisapina ta siꞌauꞌewena ga ꞌina anuwaya siluguyena, nate tolosaiyao ꞌidi sena sinabwana anuwa solanaya, ga tolosaiyao ꞌidi bodao maiboꞌadi sibwau egogonedima.  
\v 17 \x * \xo 15:17 \xt Lu 23:11\x*ꞌEnega toesaesao ꞌadi ꞌoama bweyabweyalina ꞌenega Yesu sieꞌoamena ga ꞌana peyaula kwakwakwala ꞌediyega siguinuwena ga debanaya sisaꞌuna.  
\v 18 Ga silolagata be tuyeya ꞌenega silokagutokiye, sigwaegwae, “Kamatoki ꞌoyo me Yudia ꞌidi kini ye!”   
\p
\v 19 \x * \xo 15:19 \xt Ais 50:6\x*Ta wate ꞌetoguna ꞌenega Yesu debana sisapina, ta sigiwalina, ga tuyeyega matanaya siꞌaetulasa.  
\v 20 ꞌEnega ꞌidi tuyeya ꞌigumwala, ga ꞌoama esaesa ꞌenega sialolona, ta tauna ꞌana ꞌoamega sieꞌote limena, ga siꞌauꞌewena sabi giekelosena.   
\s1 Yesu situtu epaꞌiyena kelose ꞌenaya  
\r (Madiu 27:32-44; Luke 23:26-43; Yoni 19:17-27)  
\p
\v 21 Ga ꞌasa sinabwana ꞌenega siapwesa, ga goma Sailini mitawega ꞌimeemai silobena, ga sididigena be Yesu ꞌana kelose ꞌida ꞌaali. Tai nina ꞌana esana Saimoni, ta Alekisana be Lupuso tamadiya.   
\p
\v 22 ꞌEnega siꞌauꞌewena sena Goligota ꞌenaya (Goligota ꞌana mwalatoi nate ‘Bulubulu ꞌasana’),  
\v 23 ga oine be mulo siꞌeinisena ga siꞌebwaꞌena be ꞌaene geyaꞌabo uya ꞌilotolotoo sinabwana, ta Yesu ꞌiguitoyasena.  
\v 24 \x * \xo 15:24 \xt Sam 22:18\x*ꞌEnega kelose baleꞌuya sisaꞌunaya ta Yesu ꞌenaya situtu epaꞌiyena ga sietoolona. Ga muliyega toguinuwa nidi Yesu ꞌana ꞌoamao siꞌewedi ga sieguyaiyedi taudimo ꞌediya, ta ꞌidi eguyai esasala ulaesinuwa ꞌenega, be ꞌeguma yaita ꞌinugana ꞌana ꞌoama ꞌebweu ꞌiꞌewa.   
\p
\v 25 Tuta nina Yesu sigie kelosena nate gonagona ꞌana gamwagamwana ꞌenaya.  
\v 26 Ta ꞌana kelose ꞌenaya siꞌetoladina “Me Yudia ꞌadi toloina.” Nate ꞌina mwawasa ꞌalena.   
\p
\v 27 Ta wate toꞌipwala ꞌeluwa sigie kelosedi, ꞌebweu Yesu ꞌatainaya ta ꞌebweu gegeuminaya.  
\v 28 \x * \xo 15:28 \xt Ais 53:12\x*(-)   
\p
\v 29 \x * \xo 15:29 \xt Sam 22:7; Yo 2:19\x*Ta tomota ꞌaina ꞌedega Yesu kelose ꞌena situyeyena ta siedagiyena, sigwae, “Nuwaꞌoleꞌoleyo! ꞌUona ꞌaene sawesawemuya Anuwa Tabu ꞌuligei be ꞌasiyata ꞌetoi soladiya ꞌuꞌabilima.  
\v 30 Baga ꞌuda ꞌetoseyeyo tauyo be keloseyega ꞌuebusima.”   
\p
\v 31 Ta wate totaliyao sinabwadi be loina ꞌana toeꞌitao taudimo ꞌediya sionaona gagasa, ga Yesu siꞌeetetena, sigwaegwae, “Mali tomota ꞌiꞌetoseyedi ta tauna ꞌida ꞌetoseye!  
\v 32 Tauna ꞌaene Toꞌetoseyana nina ta sena Isileli ꞌana toloina, abaga keloseyega ꞌida ebusima be taꞌita, be ꞌenega taemise.”  
\p Ta toꞌipwala nidi Yesu maꞌenao sigie kelosediya taudi ꞌadi keloseyega sibwaꞌonao ga Yesu sibaꞌena.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌimwawasa  
\r (Madiu 27:45-56; Luke 23:44-49; Yoni 19:28-30)  
\p
\v 33 Ta niꞌatu ꞌasuoleole sena maiboꞌana ꞌiguguyoi ga ꞌana laba ꞌasuinuwanuwaya,  
\v 34 \x * \xo 15:34 \xt Sam 22:1\x*ga ꞌasuinuwanuwaya Yesu ꞌenana sinabwanega ꞌibwau, ga ꞌigwae, “Eloi, eloi, lama sabakitani,” ta ꞌana gibui ꞌaene “ꞌIgu Yaubada, ꞌigu Yaubada, toꞌase manuna ꞌupilisinegu?”   
\p
\v 35 Ta ꞌaina tomota selabenaya sitootoolo ꞌina bwau sinonona ta sigwae, “Wanono, Ilaitiya ꞌibwaubwauye.”  
\v 36 \x * \xo 15:36 \xt Sam 69:21\x*ꞌEnega ꞌebweuna ꞌediyega ꞌipili ga balou ꞌiꞌewena, ga oine dalelena ꞌena ꞌietupaꞌutuina, ꞌenega ꞌebweu kaiwe ꞌena matana ꞌibadiyena ga ꞌieꞌetotuꞌeyena Yesu ꞌawanaya be ꞌisokuku, ta tai nina ꞌigwae, “Tuga tayamwayamwa, nai ꞌiabe Ilaitiya ꞌimama be keloseyega ꞌiꞌetoseye.”   
\p
\v 37 Ta Yesu ꞌibwau toitoila ga yawasina ꞌigumwala.   
\p
\v 38 \x * \xo 15:38 \xt Sia 26:31-33; Ib 10:19-20\x*Ta kaleko nina Anuwa Tabu ꞌana pitaupa ꞌiesabu luwena etanega ga ꞌimwaꞌuta ꞌubunaya.   
\p
\v 39 Ta tolosaiyao ꞌadi toanugana Yesu ꞌana kelose matanaya ꞌitootoolo Yesu ꞌina mwawasa ꞌana ꞌita gete nadigega ꞌiꞌitena, ꞌenega ꞌigwae, “Onaꞌaiꞌaila tai gote Yaubada natuna.”   
\p
\v 40 \x * \xo 15:40 \xt Lu 8:2-3\x*ꞌAina iine wate ꞌedasolega sidunedune, nate Meli Magidala be ꞌina waliyesa, tauna Yosese be tasina megwamana Yemesa sinadiya, be Salome wate,  
\v 41 taudi lowa Yesu simuliyena ta ꞌana masula siguinuwenaya ꞌina sakowasi Galili solanaya manuna, ta ꞌaina iine wate Galiliyega Yesu maꞌenao silagama Yelusalema ꞌenaya, maiboꞌadi siduneduneye.   
\s1 Yesu sisaꞌu ꞌaliꞌaliyena  
\r (Madiu 27:57-61; Luke 23:50-56; Yoni 19:38-42)  
\p
\v 42 Ta niꞌatu ꞌasuinuwa ga gibubuna mali ꞌasiyata manuna, nate me Yudia ꞌidi Sabate.  
\v 43 ꞌEnega goma Alimatia ꞌana esana Yosepa ꞌimai, tauna ꞌebweu me Yudia ꞌidi toanugana ma ꞌana emisa, ta ꞌiyamwayamwa be to tuta Yaubada baleꞌuya ꞌida etoloina. Tauna Yosepa nina ꞌimai ga ma ina ꞌatepatu ꞌilugu Pailato matanaya ga Yesu kokowana ꞌisidena be ꞌaene ꞌida saꞌuꞌaliꞌaliye.   
\b  
\p
\v 44 Ta ꞌenega Pailato ꞌilosuyaena, ꞌigwae, “Iyae! Yesu niꞌatu ꞌimwawasaya?” ꞌEnega tolosaiyao ꞌadi toanugana ꞌibwauyenama, ga ꞌimai, ga Pailato ꞌienaida, ꞌigwae, “Mwaꞌadega, Yesu niꞌatu ꞌimwawasa?”   
\p
\v 45 Ga tai nina ꞌigwae, “O, niꞌatu ꞌimwawasa.” ꞌEnega Pailato ꞌitagwala be Yosepa Yesu kokowana ꞌida ꞌewa.   
\p
\v 46 Ga Yosepa kaleko wakewakekena ꞌigimwanena ga ꞌiꞌewenama, ga ma ina toguinuwao Yesu kokowana kelose ꞌenega siꞌewa mwaꞌutenama, ga kaleko nina ꞌenega siwaduna, ga muliyega sisaꞌu ꞌaliꞌaliyena. Ta ꞌaliꞌali nina sitainaya ꞌatuwa duluwa gulewa solanaya, ta gulewa sinabwana ta pulipulina ꞌenega ꞌaliꞌali ꞌawana sisaꞌu bodena.   
\p
\v 47 Ta Meli Magidala be ꞌina waliyesa, tauna Yosese sinana, maꞌiyana sieꞌasiyedi ga ꞌaliꞌali nina ꞌena kokowana sisaꞌuna siꞌitena.   
\c 16  
\s1 Yesu ꞌina toololimana  
\r (Madiu 28:1-8; Luke 24:1-12; Yoni 20:1-10)  
\p
\v 1 ꞌEnega Sabate nina ꞌigumwala ga Meli Magidala ma ina waliyesa, tauna Yemesa sinana, be Salome wate maꞌediya bunama boboꞌana sigimwanena be ꞌaene Yesu bwalana sida eoloi.   
\p
\v 2 Ga tomwa ꞌiulisina, nate wiki ꞌana ꞌasiyata nugana ꞌenaya, ga sinala ꞌina saeꞌunu ꞌenaya iine nidi ma idi bunama simai Yesu ꞌana ꞌaliꞌali ꞌena.  
\v 3 Ga taudimo ꞌediya sionaona sigwae, “Yaita gulewa nina ꞌaliꞌali ꞌawanega ꞌida puliile manuda?” Manuna gulewa nina sinabwa wawasae.  
\v 4 Ta ꞌenega siꞌitanao ga ꞌaliꞌali ꞌana ꞌauboda gulewa niꞌatu ꞌawanega sipuli ilena siꞌitena.   
\p
\v 5 ꞌEnega iine nidi ꞌaliꞌali solanaya silugu ga ꞌataidiyega tubuwau ma ꞌana ꞌoama wakewakekena ꞌimiyami siꞌitena, ꞌenega siꞌatesaꞌala.   
\p
\v 6 Ta tubuwau nina ꞌieonedi, ꞌigwae, “Geyaꞌabo waꞌateꞌate saꞌala. Yesu goma Nasaleta tauna sigiekelosena waꞌebeꞌebese. Tauna nigeya bada, manuna niꞌatu mwawasega ꞌitoolo limana. ꞌIna ꞌebeꞌeno gete waꞌitena tuga kakaena.  
\v 7 \x * \xo 16:7 \xt Mk 14:28\x*Ta ꞌomi waila be Yesu ꞌina tononoyao ꞌediya wasisimana, ta wate Pita ꞌena wasisimana, wagwae, ‘Yesu ꞌitatauya nugana Galili ꞌena, ta ꞌomi wamuliye be gote ꞌena waꞌita, nadigega lowa ꞌina simana ꞌemiya.’ ”   
\p
\v 8 ꞌEnega iine nidi ꞌaliꞌaliyega siapwesa manini ga sidena, manuna nuwadi ꞌiowana, ta wate sidededela, ta ꞌidi matauta nigeya yaita ꞌena sisimasimane.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina apwesa Meli Magidala ꞌena  
\r (Madiu 28:9-10; Yoni 20:11-18)  
\p
\v 9 \x * \xo 16:9 \xt Lu 8:2\x*Wiki ꞌana ꞌasiyata nugana gonagonaya, Yesu ꞌina toololimana ꞌenaya ꞌigimi apwesa Meli Magidala ꞌenaya, tauna solanega lowa yaluyaluwa biꞌi site sebeni Yesu ꞌiula apwesedi.  
\v 10 ꞌEnega Meli nina ꞌitauya ga Yesu ꞌina tomotaiyao ꞌiemataluwedi, ta taudi tuga ꞌetamo ma idi nuwamwau sidedoi Yesu manuna.  
\v 11 Ta Meli emataluwa ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi ꞌigwae, “Yesu mayawasina ꞌimiyami. Niꞌatu yaꞌitena.” Ta taudi saꞌi siꞌawa kabokaboena.   
\s1 Yesu ꞌina elobaloba ꞌina tononoyao ꞌeluwa ꞌediya  
\r (Luke 24:13-35)  
\p
\v 12 Ta muliyega Yesu ꞌana tomuliyao ꞌeluwa Yelusalemega siapwesa ga mali ꞌasa manuna sitautauya, ga Yesu ꞌigie apwesena tauna mali ꞌita ꞌenega.  
\v 13 ꞌEnega site luwa nidi Yelusalema ꞌena siila ga gosediyao siemataluwedi, ta saꞌi nigeya siemiemisedi.   
\s1 Yesu ina tononoyao ꞌidi guinuwa ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi  
\r (Madiu 28:16-20; Luke 24:36-49; Yoni 20:19-23; Guinuwa 1:6-8)  
\p
\v 14 Muliyega Yesu ꞌina tononoyao site elebeni siꞌeꞌai ga Yesu matadiya ꞌiapwesa, ga ꞌiꞌenapaꞌalidi ꞌidi debapaꞌala manuna, ꞌigwae, “Gosegwao taudi ꞌigu toololimana mulinaya siꞌitegu ga ꞌemiya sisimanaya, ta mwaꞌadega ga nigeya waeemisedi?”   
\p
\v 15 Ta emataluwa ꞌiꞌebwaꞌedi, ꞌigwae, “Watatauya sena maiboꞌana ꞌediya be teteligu tomota maiboꞌadi ꞌediya waguguyae.  
\v 16 \x * \xo 16:16 \xt Gu 2:38, 16:31-33\x*ꞌEnega yaisigedi siemisegu wada giebapitaiseodi, be ꞌetoseyana sida loba, ta ꞌabo yaisigedi nigeya siemiemisa maꞌetamo loina toꞌumalina siloba.   
\p
\v 17 \x * \xo 16:17 \xt Gu 2:4, 8:7, 28:3-6; Lu 10:19\x*“Ta ꞌagu toemisao nidi weꞌiweꞌiyaya waiwaidi sida guinuwedi, nate ꞌagu esanega yaluyaluwa biꞌi tomota ꞌediyega sida ula apwesedi, be ꞌenana dumadumadi be dumadumadi ꞌediyega sida onaona,  
\v 18 be ꞌabo mwata bolabolausidi sigilagasidi geyaꞌabo ꞌidi goꞌi ꞌenega siesiesilae, be ꞌabo bwasi bolausa sinunuma geyaꞌabo simwawamwawasa, be wate ꞌabo toleꞌoasao sigitoodi sida boboꞌana tuga.”   
\s1 Yesu ꞌituꞌe galewaya  
\r (Luke 24:50-53; Guinuwa 1:9-11)  
\p
\v 19 \x * \xo 16:19 \xt Gu 2:33-34; Ep 1:20\x*ꞌIda ꞌInapwana Yesu ꞌina emataluwa ꞌediya niꞌatu ꞌilosalonina ga ꞌituꞌe galewaya, ga Yaubada ꞌatainaya ꞌimiyatowa.  
\v 20 \x * \xo 16:20 \xt Gu 14:3; Ib 2:3-4\x*Ta ꞌenega sitauya sena yauyaudi ꞌediya ga Yesu tetelina siloguguyaena, ta saꞌi ꞌInapwana maꞌedi siguiguinuwa ga ꞌina waiwaiyega guinuwa ꞌebe nuwaowanao siguinuwedi, ga ꞌenega tomota tetela nina siemisena.   